tgt_ha: 225 Smruti R. Sarangi a cikin hali. Bugu da ƙari, tunda injiniyoyin da ke aiki akan babban aikin kwamfuta na TECH> suma suna buƙatar irin waɗannan damar, yana da kyau a ƙirƙiri fasalulluka na <TECH> waɗanda za su iya rubutawa da gudanar da algorithms ɗinsu akan GPU. Da yake tsammanin irin waɗannan canje-canje, N<TECH>VIDIA sun fitar da tsarin CUDA (Compute Unified Device Architecture) a watan Fabrairun 2007, wanda shine kayan aikin haɓaka software na farko da ake samu (SDK) wanda za a iya amfani da shi don shirya GPU. Don haka, an haifi zamaniGPGPPU (generalpurposeGPU). Itisaveryprogrammableda processor mai sassauƙa wanda za a iya amfani da shi don yin kusan duk nau'ikan lissafin lambobi masu girma na TECH. GPUs a yau ba su da iyaka ga kawai sarrafawa da ƙirƙirar zane-zanen kwamfuta, maimakon haka, zane-zane ɗaya ne kawai daga cikin aikace-aikacen da GPU ke tallafawa. 6.3 Shirye-shiryen GPGPUs Kamar yadda muka gani a Sashe na 6.2, masu sarrafa zane-zane suna da tsari mai zurfi don yin ayyuka masu zurfi na zane-zane. Duk da haka, ana iya amfani da su yadda ya kamata don lambar kimiyya ta yau da kullun kamar kwaikwayon yanayi, ko lissafin rarraba yanayin zafi da abu ta amfani da dabarun nazarin abubuwa na ƙarshe. Irin waɗannan lissafin suna da halaye iri ɗaya ko ƙasa da haka. Sun haɗa da ayyuka masu rikitarwa bisa ga aljabra mai layi da kuma ayyukan lambobi da yawa. Amfani da GPUs don lissafin lambobi da kimiyya na iya yin sauti a matsayin ra'ayi bayyananne musamman bayan mun bayyana dalilin yin hakan; duk da haka, a lokacinsa, ra'ayi ne mai matuƙar juyin juya hali. Marubucin ku ya tuna da yawan shakku tsakanin mutane daga masana'antu da na ilimi lokacin da wasu masu wa'azin GPU suka fara gabatar da wannan ra'ayi. Ya ɗauki lokaci kafin a nutse. Yanzu, babu wanda ke yin kuskure idan ya ji cewa ana amfani da GPUs don babban aikin kwamfuta na TECH. A gaskiya ma, a yau GPUs na iya yin mafi yawan ɗaukar nauyi idan ana maganar aikin lissafi. A cikin wannan sashe, za mu gabatar da yaren shirye-shiryen CUDA, mu yi nazarin gine-ginensa, sannan mu rufe wasu fasaloli na ci gaba a taƙaice. Lura cewa wannan sashe yana ba da gabatarwa kawai ga harshen CUDA da lokacin gudu. Don ƙarin bayani game da magani, masu karatu ya kamata su tuntuɓi littafi a kan yaren shirye-shiryen CUDA [Farber, 2011]. 6.3.1 GPU ISAs Kamar yadda aka ambata a Sashe na 6.2.2, tsarin tattara shiri akan GPU tsari ne mai matakai biyu. Mai amfani da  yana rubuta shirinta ta amfani da nau'in C++ wanda zai iya zama ɗaya daga cikin shahararrun harsunan shirye-shiryen GPU: CUDA ko OpenCL. Bari mu bayyana kayan aikin CUDA na NVIDIA. CUDA gajeriyar hanya ce ta Compute Unified Device Architecture. Tsawaita ce ta C++ inda mai amfani da  ke rubuta shiri don dukkan layin GPU na NVIDIA. Tsarin CUDA na yau da kullun yana kama da shirin C++ tare da wasu ƙarin umarni waɗanda ke ƙayyade wane ɓangare na lambar ya kamata ya gudana akan CPU, da kuma wane ɓangare na lambar da aka yi niyya ga GPU. NVIDIA tana ba da mai tarawa na musamman da ake kira nvcc wanda za a iya amfani da shi don tattara lambar CUDA. Yana amfani da kayan aiki daban-daban don tattara lambar CPU da lambar GPU (duba Hoto na 6.8). Ana fara sarrafa lambar GPU ta hanyar mai sarrafawa na C++ wanda ke maye gurbin macros. Sannan izinin tattarawa yana tattara lambar da aka yi niyya ga GPU zuwa saitin umarnin PTX, wanda shine saitin umarni na kama-da-wane. PTX yana nufin Parallel Thread eExecution. ISA ne mai kama da RISC tare da saitin rajista marasa iyaka, inda mai tarawa ke samar da lambar galibi a cikin nau'in aiki ɗaya - kowane canji ana ba shi ƙima sau ɗaya daidai. Ta amfani da tsarin kama-da-wane ana fifita shi saboda akwai babban bambanci a cikin kayan aikin ƙasa, kuma idan muka samar da lambar don nau'in kayan aiki ɗaya, lambar za ta rasa sauƙin ɗauka. Daga baya, muna samar da wani nau'in binary mai kitse, wanda ke ɗauke da lambar PTX, kuma yana ɗauke da lambar injin don samfuran GPU daban-daban masu shahara. A takaice dai, binary guda ɗaya yana ɗauke da hotuna daban-daban, inda kowane hoto ya dace da takamaiman GPUISA. A lokaci guda, muna tattara ɓangaren C++ na lambar ta amfani da daidaitattun masu haɗa C++, muna saka nassoshi ga ayyukan GPU, da ayyukan haɗin gwiwa da ɗakin karatu na CUDA ya bayar. a ƙarshe nvcc yana samar da aiwatarwa ɗaya wanda ya ƙunshi duka CPU da lambar GPU.

An yi nufin wannan takarda don taimaka wa masu haɓakawa da masu amfani da ƙarshen fahimtar buƙatun HFR na aiki da waɗanda ba su aiki ba. Sauran albarkatu don tallafawa aiwatar da Babban Jerin Kayan Aikin Najeriya suna samuwa a nan: a cikin Najeriya/. Takardu Yarjejeniyar Takardu An shirya waɗannan ƙayyadaddun buƙatun software na HFR bisa ga ƙa'idodin injiniyan software da tsarin na Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE). Kowane tsarin  buƙatar an sanya masa lambar buƙatun  ta musamman da matakin fifiko. Fifiko ga buƙatun manyan matakai sun ba da damar haɓaka cikakkun buƙatu. Shawarwari Kan Masu Sauraro da Karatu: Mutane masu ƙwarewa daban-daban za su iya amfani da wannan takarda don manufofinsu, kamar haka: • Masu Haɓakawa: Wannan rukunin zai yi amfani da takardar don fahimtar ƙayyadaddun buƙatun fasaha da kuma yadda za a canza su zuwa tsarin  lokacin da aka rubuta aikace-aikacen software na ƙarshe na <TECH>. • Masu Gwaji: Wannan rukunin zai yi amfani da takardar yayin gwajin raka'a da gwajin haɗin gwiwa na <TECH>tsarin don fahimtar duk fasalulluka na tsarin  da kuma yadda tsarin <TECH> yake amsawa ga abubuwan da ke motsawa na waje. • Masu amfani na ƙarshe: Masu amfani na ƙarshe na <TECH>tsarin za su fi sha'awar cikakken bayanin HFR, wanda zai taimaka musu su fahimci samfurin HFR na ƙarshe wanda masu haɓakawa da masu gwaji za su isar kuma su iya gabatar da wasu buƙatu waɗanda ƙungiyar haɓaka za ta iya rasa. Faɗin Samfura HFR da za a tsara don Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta Tarayya zai zama tashar yanar gizo mai buɗewa wacce ke nuna duk asibitoci, asibitoci, cibiyoyin daukar hoto, da dakunan gwaje-gwaje a Najeriya. Tsarin tsarin zai ba masu amfani da izini damar kamawa da adana bayanan wurin aiki. Za a tsara tsarin  don bai wa masu amfani damar saukewa da fitar da Bayanai a cikin tsare-tsare daban-daban don dalilai daban-daban. A. Tushen Tsarin Halittu Nazarin da ke bayyana alaƙar da ke tsakanin dukkan halittu na halitta da muhallinsu ana kiransa da Ilimin Halittu. Duk waɗannan yanayi, yanayi da tasirin da ke shafar ci gaban wani halitta ko ƙungiyar halittu sune muhalli. Don haka, ilimin muhalli da muhalli suna da alaƙa da juna a cikin mahallin halittu da tsarin da ke shafar su. A fannin yanki, musayar abu tsakanin ƙasa da teku yana gudana ta hanyar manyan hanyoyin ilimin halitta guda biyu. Hulɗar da ke tsakanin mutum da yanayi ba za a iya raba ta ba. Ita ce mafi girman nau'in hulɗa tsakanin rayuwa gabaɗaya da muhalli musamman. Bambancin nau'ikan rayuwa da suka samo asali tsawon ɗaruruwan shekaru kuma rungumarsu zuwa yanayi daban-daban, sau da yawa mawuyacin hali, abin mamaki ne. Hulɗar ɗan adam da yanayi ta fara ne a lokacin da suka rabu da muhallin halitta. Dangantaka tsakanin mutum da yanayi tana ɗaukar siffarsa a cikin mazauninsa. Kwarewar hulɗar ɗan adam da yanayi aiki ne na tsarawa na da. Don yin amfani da yanayi mafi kyau, mutum yana yin gyare-gyare da suka wajaba a cikin tsarin muhalli. Kula da dabbobin daji, zaɓar shuke-shuke masu amfani daga shuke-shuken halitta, yin baranda a kan gangaren tsaunuka, daidaita koguna don ban ruwa ko shawo kan ambaliyar ruwa da sauransu misalai ne na tsara jin daɗin mutane yayin da ake daidaita yanayin muhalli. An tsara gidajen ɗan adam kusa da hanyoyin ruwa, wuraren aiki da kuma la'akari da aminci da motsi. Yawancin manyan ayyukan kamar noma, noma, noma, da sauransu sun dogara ne akan la'akari da yanayin aiki. Hakazalika, wasu daga cikin tsarin samarwa na sakandare kamar software, takarda, da sauran masana'antu masu sassaucin ra'ayi da sauransu an tsara su ta hanyar da za ta haifar da aƙalla 6 GEOGRAPHY

tgt_ha: 2.2 Siffofin Samfura Wannan sashe zai gabatar da cikakken bayani game da fasalulluka na aikace-aikacen SSA . Za a ƙara yin bayani game da waɗannan ayyuka a Sashe na 3 na wannan takaddun. 1. Shigarwa mai hulɗa da samar da rubutu SSA zai sami hanyar sadarwa mai hulɗa wanda ke ba wa ɗalibi damar yin tambayoyi na gabaɗaya ga aikace-aikacen  ko kuma ya ba shi umarni. SSA zai yi amfani da NLP don sarrafa shigarwar rubutu ko murya da aka yi rikodin, kuma zai yi amfani da ƙwarewar samar da rubutu don samar da amsa. 2. Gudanar da Lokaci Aikace-aikacen SSA  zai ba wa ɗalibai taimakon sarrafa lokaci. Misali, zai iya saita tunatarwa don mahimman wa'adin lokaci, don samar da jadawalin azuzuwan da ayyuka, ko samar wa ɗalibi tsarin karatu na musamman bisa ga buƙatunsu. 3. Shawarwarin lafiya da motsa jiki SSA zai sami zaɓin zaɓi na ba wa ɗalibi shawarwari game da manufofin lafiya da wasanni. Idan aka yi amfani da shi, wannan aikin zai samar wa ɗalibi da tunatarwa kamar shawarwari game da alƙawarin likitan hakori na gaba, ƙarin alluran rigakafi daban-daban, ko haɗa ayyukan motsa jiki a cikin jadawalin aikinsu. 4. Taimakon babban mataki tare da aikin ilimi SSA zai iya ba wa ɗalibai taimako mai girma game da aikinsu na ilimi. Ana haɓaka wannan aikin ta hanyar bincika manufofin lagiarism na UCD P kuma dole ne a tabbatar da cewa an sanya kariya don guje wa haɗarin ɗabi'a da satar bayanai. Bugu da ƙari, wannan aikin zai ba ɗalibai damar samar da taƙaitaccen taƙaitaccen bayani game da ƙananan batutuwa daban-daban na kayan aikinsu. 5. Haɗa SSA tare da kayan aikin UCD, ChatGPT, tsarin Tsaro , da kuma Basebase Za a haɗa SSA cikin sauƙi tare da kayan aikin ilimi na UCD (kalanda, jadawalin lokaci, wa'adin lokaci, kayan kwas) don ba shi damar yin ayyukan da aka ambata a sama. Hakazalika, za ta sami fasalin ChatGPT da aka gina a ciki don kunna ayyukanta, kuma za a haɗa ta da rumbun adana bayanai na  don ba wa masu amfani damar adana bayanan  da ci gaba. 2.3 Darussa da Halayen  Mai Amfani Za a tsara SSA  don ɗaliban aji na <TECH> mai amfani, duka a matakin digiri na farko da na digiri na biyu. An tsara aikace-aikacen  musamman don ɗaliban da suka yi rajista a UCD. 2.4 Muhalli na Aiki Za a tsara SSA don ya dace da tsarin aiki na wayar hannu da aka fi amfani da shi, wato Android da iOS. Ganin ayyukan aikace-aikacen , SSA kuma za a samar da shi akan masu binciken yanar gizo da aka fi amfani da su akan tsarin aiki na tebur, kamar macOS, Windows, da Unix. Wannan ya kamata ya ba da damar ayyukan taimakon ilimi su fi dacewa ga ɗalibai, domin za su iya samun damar shiga wannan fasalin kai tsaye akan kwamfutocinsu.

tgt_ha: Ciki na Duniya da Kayanta - 2 Canjin fuska na 2.2 Tsarin Cikin Duniya Zane na sama (duba hoto na 2.1) yana nuna layukan ciki na duniya mai ma'ana. Layer na ciki da ke kewaye da tsakiyar duniya ana kiransa tsakiya, wanda yake kimanin kilomita 3500 a radius. Core shine Layer mafi yawan duniya tare da yawansa daga 9.5 zuwa 14.5 kuma wani lokacin ma mafi girma. Ya ƙunshi galibin ƙarfe da nickel na Notes wanda aka fi sani da Nife. (Nickel+Ferrum). Core ya ƙunshi layuka biyu. Na ciki yana da ƙarfi (C na hoto na 2.1) kuma na waje shine ruwa mai rabin-2 (C na hoto na 2.1). Layer da ke kewaye da tsakiya ana kiransa mantle, harsashi mai dutse 1 mai kauri kusan kilomita 2900 kuma ya ƙunshi silicates na asali. Manyan abubuwan da ke cikin mantle sune magnesium da silicon, saboda haka, ana kiran wannan Layer da Sima (Silica+Magnesium). Yawan wannan Layer ya bambanta daga 3.3 zuwa 5.7. Mantle yana kewaye da mafi girman Layer na duniya, wanda aka sani da lithosphere kuma yawansa ya bambanta daga 2.70 zuwa 2.95. Manyan abubuwan da ke cikin lithosphere sune silica (Si) da aluminum (Al), don haka ana kiran wannan Layer da Sial (Silica+Aluminum). Mafi girman ɓangaren lithosphere a cikin da aka sani da ɓawon burodi, yawanci kusan kauri kilomita 8 zuwa 40.  Core, mantle da ɓawon burodi sune manyan layuka uku na cikin duniya.  Core shine Layer na ciki kuma yana da mafi girman yawa. Ya ƙunshi galibin nickel da ƙarfe.  Mantle shine Layer da ke tsakanin tsakiya da lithosphere. Manyan abubuwan da ke cikinsa sune silicon da magnesium.  Ƙashin ƙasa shine mafi girman ɓangaren duniya kuma galibi yana ƙunshe da silicon da aluminum. TAMBAYOYIN JARIDA 2.1 1. tgt_ha: Teku: Rage Ruwa a ƙarƙashin Ruwa da Tsarin Zagayawa a Ruwa - 3 Yankin kwararar ruwa 8.5 na Tekun Atlantika a Duniya A arewa da kudu na equator akwai kwararar ruwa guda biyu masu motsi a yamma wato, kwararar ruwa ta arewa da kudu. Tsakanin waɗannan kwararar ruwa guda biyu akwai kwararar ruwa ta Counter Equator</TECH> wadda ke gudana daga yamma zuwa gabas. (Nemo ta a cikin hoto na 8.10). Wannan kwararar ruwa ta counter ta maye gurbin Bayanan da aka cire daga gefen gabas na teku ta hanyar kwararar ruwa ta Arewa da Kudu ta Equator. Kudancin Equator ya rabu zuwa rassan biyu kusa da Cape De Sao Roque a Brazil. Reshenta na arewa ya haɗu da kwararar ruwa ta Arewa ta Equator</TECH>. Wannan kwararar ruwa ta haɗu ta shiga Tekun Caribbean da Tekun Mexico, yayin da sauran kwararar ruwa ta ratsa gabashin Yammacin Indies a matsayin Antilles Current. Sashen kwararar ruwa da ke shiga Tekun Mexico, yana fitowa daga mashigar Florida kuma ya haɗu da kwararar ruwa ta Antilles Current. Wannan hadadden kwararar ruwa yana tafiya a gefen kudu maso gabashin Amurka. Ana kiransa da Florida Current har zuwa cape of Hatteras. Bayan Cape Hatteras, har zuwa Grand Banks, kusa da New Foundland, ana kiransa Gulf Stream. Daga Grand Banks, Gulf Stream yana karkata zuwa gabas a ƙarƙashin haɗin gwiwar yammacin duniya da kuma juyawar duniya. Yana ketare Tekun Atlantika a matsayin North Atlantic Drift. Hoto na 8.10 Ruwa na Tekun Atlantika Ruwa na Arewacin Atlantika Ruwa na Arewacin Atlantika ya rabu zuwa rassan biyu yayin da ya isa gabashin teku. Reshen arewa yana ci gaba da zama North Atlantic Drift; ya isa Tsibirin Burtaniya daga inda yake gudana a bakin tekun Norway a matsayin Norwegian Current kuma ya shiga Tekun Arctic. Reshen kudu yana gudana tsakanin Spain da Azores Island a matsayin Canaries Current mai sanyi. Canaries Current a ƙarshe ya haɗu da North Equatorial Current kuma ya kammala GEOGRAPHY 151

tgt_ha: 711 Smruti R. Sarangi Don haka za mu iya wakiltar aikin juyawa kamar haka: (cid:88)(cid:88)(cid:88) O[n][k][h][w]= I[n][c][h+r][w+s]×F[k][c][r][s] (14.6) c r s Muna yin sauƙaƙawa da yawa a cikin wannan lissafi. Mun cire jeri na maimaitawa, kuma na biyu muna ɗauka cewa aikin an ayyana shi ne don pixels a gefunan hoton. Yi la'akari da pixel a ƙasan dama O[H −1][W −1]. Ba a ayyana aikin juyawa ba don wannan pixel saboda yawancin pixels da ake buƙatar la'akari da su don juyawa ba su wanzu. A wannan yanayin, yawanci ana yin zato mai sauƙi inda muke ɗauka cewa akwai ƙarin abubuwa a bayan gefunan ƙasa da dama waɗanda ke ɗauke da sifili. Wannan an san shi da sifili. Bugu da ƙari, muna lura cewa ga kowane hoton shigarwa, muna ƙididdige juyawa. Kowace pixel na taswira ta dogara ne akan dukkan taswirorin da aka shigar (gabaɗaya), da kuma taswirar da aka riga aka haɗa taswira. Wannan shine daidaitaccen daidaito na juyawa, wanda ke ba mu damar guje wa lissafi mai nauyi tare da manyan vectors masu nauyi. Irin waɗannan hanyoyin sadarwa na jijiyoyi masu juyawa ana kiransu CNNs, kuma sun tabbatar da cewa suna da matuƙar amfani a fannoni daban-daban. Tsarin CNN Muna da nau'ikan yadudduka guda huɗu a cikin CNN: Layer convolutional, Layer completely connected, ReLU Layer, da pooling Layer. Layer biyu na ƙarshe sune yadudduka marasa layi. An nuna misalin ƙirar CNN a Hoto na 14.4 wanda ke nuna duk waɗannan layukan. W W S H H R CONV2D 2D convolution ReLU Rectified linear unit K Pooling Max. connecting CK of taswira FC Layer complete connected Layer C filters iftaps CONV2D ReLU Pooling CONV2D ReLU FC Fitar da fitarwa Hoto Hoto na 14.4: Tsarin CNN Daga mahangar lissafi, ReLU da connecting Layers suna da sauƙin sarrafawa. Ba mu buƙatar wata dabara mai zurfi don fahimtar ayyukansu, kuma aiwatar da su ƙaramin ɓangare ne na jimlar aiwatarwa. Tsarin da aka haɗa gaba ɗaya yana da nauyi dangane da sawun ƙwaƙwalwarsa da kuma nauyin lissafi. Duk da haka, tunda muna da irin wannan Layer ɗaya kawai a cikin hanyar sadarwa mai zurfi ta jijiyoyi kuma yana samar da wasu sakamako kaɗan, lokacin aiwatarwarsa ba shi da damuwa musamman. Kusan duk binciken da aka yi a CNN an sadaukar da shi ne don hanzarta matakan juyin halitta waɗanda suka kai fiye da kashi 90% na jimlar lokacin aiwatarwa. Za mu mai da hankali kan hanyoyin juyin halitta da tattaunawa kan hanyoyi daban-daban don inganta aiwatar da su.

tgt_ha: 587 Smruti R. Sarangi Layin Bit Layi kyauta Layi mai ɗaure Layi Layi Zaɓi layi Hoto na 10.33: Tsarin tantanin MRAM [Kawahara et al., 2012] tsarin tsara tantanin halitta. Ka tuna cewa lokacin da tantanin halitta yake a cikin yanayin layi ɗaya (P) (alkiblar maganadisu iri ɗaya ne), muna adana ma'ana 1; lokacin da tantanin halitta yake a cikin yanayin anti-parallel (AP) (babban juriya), muna adana ma'ana 0. Don canzawa daga AP zuwa yanayin P, electrons suna buƙatar gudana daga layin da aka ɗaure zuwa layin kyauta. Wannan saboda yayin da suke wucewa ta cikin layin da aka ɗaure juyawarsu suna samun polarized (yawancinsu a cikin hanya ɗaya). Daga baya, yayin da suke ratsa ta cikin layin MgO, kuma suna shiga layin kyauta, suna canja wurin wasu daga cikin ƙarfin juyawa don yin maganadisu a cikin layin kyauta a cikin alkiblar layin da aka ɗaure. Don cimma wannan, muna buƙatar samun layin bit a mafi girma idan aka kwatanta da layin zaɓi don haka kwararar wutar lantarki daga layin bit zuwa layin zaɓi. Yanzu don matsawa daga yanayin P zuwa AP, muna wuce electrons a juyi - daga layin kyauta zuwa layin da aka manne. Ana samun wannan ta hanyar saita yuwuwar layin zaɓi sama da layin bit. A wannan yanayin, electrons suna wucewa ta layin kyauta da farko. Elektrons waɗanda ke da juyi iri ɗaya kamar alkiblar magnetization a cikin layin da aka manne ba tare da wata matsala ba suna wucewa ta cikin tsari. Duk da haka, wani ɓangare na electrons waɗanda ba su da alkiblar juyawa iri ɗaya, suna komawa baya. Suna samun haske daga iyakar layin da aka manne MgO. A hankali, ƙarin electrons suna taruwa a cikin layin kyauta. Suna canja wurin ƙarfin juyi zuwa electrons a cikin layin kyauta, kuma alkiblar magnetization a cikin layin kyauta yana juyawa. Don haka, magnetization na layin kyauta yana canza alkiblarsa, kuma tantanin halitta yana shiga yanayin AP. Ribobi da Fursunoni Tantanin halitta na STT-MRAM yana da fa'idodi da yawa. Wutar leaking, wanda shine wutar da ke gudana ta cikin tantanin halitta ko da lokacin da ba ta aiki ba kusan sifili ne. Kamar yadda za mu gani a Babi na 11, wannan ba shine lamarin a cikin tunanin SRAM da DRAM na al'ada ba. A gare su, ana iya cire ƙarfin ikon amfani da wutar lantarki gaba ɗaya. Bugu da ƙari, buƙatun yanzu don karanta ko rubuta tantanin halitta na STT-MRAM ba su da yawa. Babban rashin amfani da wannan na'urar shine cewa ba ta da sauri kamar tantanin halitta na gargajiya na DRAM. Dalilin
label: NFR

tgt_ha: Guguwar guguwa ce mai ƙarfi da ke zagaye, inda iska mai sauri ke busawa daga waje zuwa tsakiya kuma tana da alaƙa da ruwan sama mai ƙarfi. Guguwar tana taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin zagayawar sararin samaniya gaba ɗaya. Guguwar da ta ci gaba sosai za ta iya canja wurin tan biliyan 3.5 na iska mai dumi cikin awa ɗaya. Yaushe guguwa ke faruwa? Guguwar wani abu ne da ke faruwa. Tana mai da hankali ne ga wasu sassan zagayowar yanayi. A Indiya, yawancin guguwar suna faruwa ne a lokacin bayan damina, wato daga Oktoba zuwa Disamba ko kuma a lokacin kafin damina daga Afrilu zuwa Mayu. Tsawon rayuwar guguwar yawanci yana daga kwanaki 7 zuwa 14. Motsin Guguwar Guguwar, tare da tsarinta na gaba ɗaya na TECH, tana tafiya gaba daga gabas zuwa yamma (a Bay of Bengal) da saurin kilomita 15 zuwa 30 a kowace awa. Guguwar da ta afka wa Orissa, ta samo asali ne kusa da Tsibirin Andaman & Nicobar kuma ta isa Orissa a ranar 29-10-1999 bayan kwanaki da yawa. Motsin guguwar zuwa wani alkibla kamar motsi ne na saman teku mai juyawa. Guguwar guguwa ta samo asali ne daga saman teku kuma tana wargajewa yayin da take isa ƙasa. Ina guguwar ke afkawa a Indiya Gabashin Indiya shine yankin da guguwar ta fi shafa. Jihohin da guguwar ta fi shafa sune; West Bengal, Orissa, Andhra Pradesh da Tamil Nadu: Gabar yamma tana shafar guguwar da ta samo asali daga Tekun Larabawa. Gujarat a gabar yamma, guguwar ta fi shafar ta. Yankunan bakin teku da cikin Maharstra suma guguwar ta shafa. Guguwar ta fi samo asali ne daga Tekun Bengal da Tekun Arabain fiye da kowace teku ta duniya. Barnar guguwar guguwar iska mai ƙarfi ta lalata duk abin da ya taso daga hanyarsu; gida mai rufin ƙasa zuwa fada, sansanonin da aka gina da siminti, ƙarfe da duwatsu. An cire bishiyoyi. Layukan wutar lantarki da sadarwa sun lalace. Ruwan sama mai ƙarfi yana haifar da ambaliya. Ambaliyar ruwa tana lalata ko'ina. Ana haifar da raƙuman ruwa masu ƙarfi a cikin teku ta hanyar iska mai sauri. Suna afkawa yankunan bakin teku kamar babban bango kuma suna mamaye yankunan har zuwa kilomita 10-15 daga bakin teku. A waɗannan yankunan gidaje, amfanin gona, hanyoyi, gine-gine, ƙauyuka da birane duk sun nutse. Zaftarewar ƙasa da ruwan sama mai ƙarfi ya haifar ya fi muni. Ƙasashen da suka ci gaba sun ƙirƙiro matakai don rage zafin guguwa. Ana bayar da gargaɗin guguwar. Ana watsa su kuma ana watsa su ta talabijin a lokacin da ya dace. Wannan yana ceton rayukan mutane. Akasin haka, mutanen da ke ƙasashe masu tasowa suna mutuwa da wuri. A Amurka, wata guguwa mai ƙarfi mai suna Hugho ta afkawa a watan Satumba na 1989. Mutane 21 ne kawai suka rasa rayukansu saboda tasirinta, saboda an bayar da ɗumamar yanayi, amma akasin haka, mutane 1,39,000 ne suka rasa rayukansu a Bangladesh lokacin da guguwar ta afkawa ƙasar a shekarar 1991.

tgt_ha: 97 Smruti R. Sarangi mun ƙara lambar sigar. Lura cewa ana amfani da wannan lambar a cikin misalanmu na gudu don manufar ƙarin bayani. A cikin tsarin na gaske, ana yin lambar daban (duba Sashe na 4.1.5). Duk da iyakokin tsarinmu mai sauƙi, mun lura a sarari cewa lambar da aka sake wa suna tana da dogaro ɗaya kawai (tsakanin Layi na 2 da 3), wanda dogaro ne na RAW. Ba sai an faɗi ba, yayin wannan aikin gine-gine zuwa rajista na zahiri, daidaiton shirin bai shafi ba. Alaƙar mai samarwa da mai amfani tsakanin umarni ya kasance. Lambar tana kama da an tattara ta ne don na'ura wacce a zahiri tana da adadi mai yawa na rajista. Muna buƙatar tabbatar da cewa haka lamarin yake, lokacin da muka tattauna aiwatarwa mafi gaskiya. Lambar asali An sake suna lambar 1 ƙara r1, r2, r3 ƙara p11, p2, p3 1 2 ƙara r1, r4, r5 /* WAW dep. r1 */ ƙara p12, p4, p5 2 3 ƙara r6, r1, r7 /* RAW dep. r1 */ ƙara p61, p12, p7 3 4 ƙara r7, r8, r9 /* WAR dep. r7 */ ƙara p71, p8, p9 4 Hoto na 4.1: Lambar asali da aka sake wa suna Yanzu, a aikace, ba za mu taɓa samun adadin rajista marasa iyaka ba. Duk da haka, bari mu yi niyya ga yanayi, inda ba za mu taɓa gaza rajistar zahiri ba. A wannan yanayin, adadin irin waɗannan rajistar zahiri kusan ba shi da iyaka. Wannan kyakkyawan hangen nesa ne, kuma duk muna son samun tsarin wanda ba ya kawar da tasirin <TECH>aikin na magance haɗarin WAW da WAR. Duk da haka, kafin mu ci gaba, muna buƙatar amsa tambaya ta asali: "Wa ke yin sake suna?" Bari mu yi la'akari da abin da muka riga muka sani game da wannan batu. Ka tuna cewawehadarguedinBabi na 2 cewa bai kamata mai shirye-shiryen ya sani ba idan mai sarrafawa yana cikin tsari ko kuma ya fita daga tsari. Mai shirye-shiryen yana buƙatar ganin irin wannan ra'ayi na rajista, wanda shine saitin rajistar gine-gine. Duk wani rajista na zahiri dole ne a ayyana shi kawai a cikin mai sarrafawa, kuma dole ne ya kasance a bayyane ga abubuwan da ke cikin mai sarrafawa kawai. Rijistar zahiri ya kamata ta zama ra'ayi mara fayyace a wajen mai sarrafawa. Wannan tattaunawar ta hanyar halitta tana amsa tambayar, "Wa ke yin sake suna?" Amsar ita ce mai sarrafawa yana yin sa, ba tare da sanin mai shirye-shiryen da mai tarawa ba. Duk haɗarin WAR da WAW ana kawar da su ta hanyar mai sarrafawa da kansa, kuma babu wani haɗin gwiwa da ƙungiyoyin software kamar mai tarawa ke buƙata. Wannan gaba ɗaya yana cikin mai sarrafawa. Don haka bari mu ci gaba da amsa tambaya ta gaba, "Ta yaya mai sarrafawa ke sake suna umarni?" 4.1.2 Sake suna ta amfani da Rijistar Jiki Bari mu yi la'akari da ISA na yau da kullun wanda ke da rajistar gine-gine 16. Bari mu ɗauka cewa akwai rajistar jiki 128 da ake amfani da su don yin sake suna. Wannan yana nufin cewa wani yanki na lambar da ke amfani da rajistar gine-gine an canza shi zuwa wani yanki na lambar daidai da ke amfani da rajistar zahiri. Sakamakon ƙarshe na duka kayan aikin "soft" yana aiki daidai. Duk da haka, kamar yadda aka ambata a Babi na 2, lambar da ke da rajistar zahiri tana aiki da sauri saboda ba ta da haɗarin WAR da WAW. Ma'ana 18 Fayil ɗin rajista na zahiri saitin rajista ne a cikin mai sarrafawa. Ana amfani da kowane rajista na zahiri don manufar sake suna. Ba a ganin rajistar zahiri ga software ko wani abu a wajen mai sarrafawa.

tgt_ha: - Abu na uku, ɗalibi ya kamata ya sami damar ƙara ƙarin abubuwa a kalandarsa ko jadawalin aikinsa, don ba shi damar haɗa duk wani taron da ba na jami'a ba a cikin aikace-aikacen . - Abu na huɗu, aikace-aikacen  ya kamata</TECH> ya kasance yana da fasalin da zai ba ɗalibai damar tsara jadawalin mako-mako ta atomatik bisa ga jadawalin  na yau da kullun, da kuma duk wani ƙarin ayyuka da ɗalibi ke son haɗawa da su (wasanni, alƙawuran likita, lokacin karatu, da sauransu). 3.2.3 Bukatun Aiki - Dole ne  ya kasance a bayyane a cikin hanyar sadarwa wanda ke nuna zaɓuɓɓukan sarrafa lokaci daban-daban. - Dole ne <TECH> ya kasance a cikin hanyar shigarwa don ɗalibi don shigar da ƙarin abubuwan da suka faru da ayyuka waɗanda ba a haɗa su kai tsaye daga kayan aikin UCD ba. - Dole ne <TECH> ya kasance a cikin hanyar daidaitawa don ba da damar SSA don samun damar <TECH> da kuma nuna kalandar UCD, jadawalin lokaci, da jerin wa'adin lokaci kai tsaye a cikin aikace-aikacen <TECH>. - Aikace-aikacen  dole ne ya ƙunshi shirin da ke ba wa ɗalibi damar samar da mai tsara shirin sa na mako-mako daidai da buƙatunsa. - Dole ne  ya kasance wata hanya don ƙirƙirar tunatarwa da faɗakarwa game da abubuwan da suka faru na <TECH> waɗanda ke gargaɗin ɗalibai yadda ya kamata (idan aka yi la'akari da nakasa mai yiwuwa na <TECH>mai amfani). - Dole ne  ya haɗa da akwatin shigarwa / fitarwa don yin tambayoyi a shafin farko na aikace-aikacen <TECH>. - Tsarin shigarwar ya kamata ya haɗa da damar shigar da murya da kuma samun aikace-aikacen   ya karanta. 3.3 Shawarwarin Lafiya da Motsa Jiki 3.3.1 Bayani da Fifikon fasalin SSA za ta sami zaɓi na samar wa masu amfani da ita shawarwari game da manufofin lafiya da wasanni. Ganin cewa wannan aikin ba shi da alaƙa kai tsaye da nasarar ilimi na masu amfani, za a aiwatar da shi azaman zaɓi. Idan an yi amfani da shi, wannan aikin zai samar wa ɗalibi da fasaloli kamar tunatarwa game da alƙawarin likitan hakori na gaba, ƙarin allurar rigakafi daban-daban, haɗa ayyukan jiki a cikin jadawalin aikinsu, da sauran shawarwari makamancin haka. Fifiko - Matsakaici 3.3.2 Jerin abubuwan ƙarfafawa / Amsawa - A lokacin saita aikace-aikacen SSA , za a tambayi masu amfani ko suna son kunna shawarwarin Lafiya da Motsa Jiki. Idan suka zaɓi kada su yi, har yanzu ana iya juyawa wannan a cikin wani shafin da aka keɓe na aikace-aikacen . - Idan mai amfani da  ya zaɓi yin amfani da wannan fasalin, za a nemi su cike tambayoyin farko da suka shafi lafiyarsu ta yanzu, manufofin lafiyarsu, manufofin lafiyarsu, halaye masu dacewa, da lokacin shawarwarin lafiya na musamman (likitan hakora, allurar rigakafi, da sauransu). - Dangane da amsoshin tambayoyin, za a kammala sashen kula da lokaci na aikace-aikacen  tare da ƙarin abubuwan da suka shafi lafiya da lafiyar mai amfani da  (misali, tunatarwa don ganin likitan haƙori duk bayan watanni 6, don yin ƙarin allurar rigakafi, zuwa wurin motsa jiki, da sauransu). - Shawarwarin motsa jiki na musamman, kamar tsare-tsaren motsa jiki ko shawarwarin abinci za su kasance a cikin sashin da aka keɓe na aikace-aikacen . Dangane da shawarwarin abinci, aikace-aikacen  zai kuma gabatar da jerin siyayya da takamaiman menu na mako-mako waɗanda ke la'akari da manufofin mai amfani. 3.3.3 Bukatun Aiki - Ya kamata a ƙirƙiri tambayoyin farko  tare da taimakon ƙwararrun likitoci.

tgt_ha: Babi na 1 1. Gabatarwa 1.1 Manufa Wannan takardar Bayanin Bukatun Software tana ba da cikakken bayani game da halayen "Goge Buɗebravo tsarin ERP  a cikin harshen Sinhala kuma aiwatar da shi tare da tsarin jami'a <TECH>" wanda za a haɓaka, tare da la'akari da ayyukansa na ciki da na waje da kuma iyawarsa. A ƙarƙashin wannan mafita da aka gabatar a nan yana bayyana game da Gudanar da Sayayya. Galibi duk buƙatun masu amfani, buƙatun tsarin <TECH> (Bayyana abin da ya kamata a aiwatar da <TECH>), buƙatun aiki da waɗanda ba na aiki ba waɗanda aka yi nufin aiwatarwa a cikin samfurin an ƙayyade su a cikin wannan takarda. Tunda an ba da cikakken bayani game da aikin da software ɗin da aka gabatar zai yi a cikin wannan takarda, wannan zai taimaka wa masu karatu da masu amfani su tantance ko software ɗin da aka ƙayyade da gaske yana magance matsalar da ke faruwa a yanzu da kuma ko ya cika buƙatun al'ummar da aka yi niyya. Sannan ya tattauna yadda tsarin <TECH> da aka gabatar ya bambanta da waɗannan hanyoyin. An rubuta wannan ne da nufin samar da fahimtar da ta dace game da Gudanar da Sayayya, fasalinsa, ƙananan sassansa, yadda kowace ƙananan sassan ke aiki da kuma alaƙar da ke tsakanin waɗannan ƙananan sassan ga masu haɓaka masu amfani da ƙarshen da waɗanda ke da sha'awar wannan fanni na bincike. A cikin wannan takarda, an nuna tsarin <TECH> a cikin zane don sa masu karatu su ga ya fi sauƙi su fahimta kuma an gabatar da shi ta hanyar da ta fi sauƙi don magance masu sauraro masu matakai daban-daban na ƙwarewar fasaha da ilimin da ya dace. 1.2 Faɗin Wannan fannin bincike yana mai da hankali kan ba wa masu amfani ƙwarewar tsara albarkatu mafi kyau a cikin yaren Sinhala, waɗanda ke fama da hanyoyin Tsarin Albarkatun Kasuwanci (ERP). Wannan takarda tana da alaƙa da buƙatun mai amfani da kuma tsarin buƙatar na mafita da aka gabatar da aikace-aikacen gidan yanar gizo na ERP  wanda za a haɓaka a ƙarƙashin ra'ayin bincike da aka ambata a baya. tgt_ha: 377 Smruti R. Sarangi Routing a cikin Zobba Bari mu miƙa wannan sakamakon zuwa zoben N-node, inda ƙa'idodi marasa amfani za su iya samun makullan ƙarewa (duba Misali na 7). Bugu da ƙari, ba za a iya amfani da hanyar X-Y a cikin zobba ba saboda babu axis na y. Za mu iya amfani da hanyar da ta dogara da layin kwanan wata ta amfani da tashoshi biyu na kama-da-wane. Bari mu fayyace layin kwanan wata tsakanin nodes 1 da 2. A wannan yanayin, yana da sauƙi a faɗaɗa shaidar Theorem 8.3.6.1 don nuna cewa irin wannan algorithm ta amfani da tashoshi biyu na kama-da-wane ba shi da makullan ƙarewa. Misali na 7 Nuna cewa yana yiwuwa a sami makullan ƙarewa a cikin zobe inda tsarin hanyar koyaushe yana tilasta juyawa zuwa alkiblar agogo. A ɗauka cewa muna da VC guda ɗaya a kowace tashar zahiri a alkiblar agogo kuma kowane VC yana da makullan k. Amsa: Yi la'akari da tsarin sadarwa mai zuwa. Node i yana ƙoƙarin aika k flits zuwa node (i+2)%N (lambobi suna ƙaruwa a alkiblar agogo). Bari mu gabatar da mai aiki + , wanda aka bayyana N kamar haka: a+ b=(a+b)%N. Ga '%' shine sauran ko mai aiki modulo. N Yanzu la'akari da jerin abubuwan da ke tafe. Kowace node i tana aika k flits daga node i zuwa i+ 1. N Duk thenodes suna yin wannan a lokaci guda. Daga baya, duk wani givennodei ba zai iya yin ci gaba ba saboda tashar da ke tsakanin i+ 1 da i+ 2 tana ɗauke da flits da ake aika daga node i+ 1. N N N Don haka, flit ɗin yana toshewa. A cikin CDG daidai akwai kibiya tsakanin tashar (cid:104)i,i+ 1(cid:105), N da (cid:104)i+ 1,i+ 2(cid:105). Lura cewa muna da irin waɗannan dogaro ga duk i, kuma wannan yana haifar da zagayowar a cikin N N CDG. Babu wani juyi da zai iya motsawa zuwa tashar sa ta biyu a kan hanya saboda an toshe wannan tashar. Wannan juyi ne na ƙarshe. Juyi a Tori Bari mu yi la'akari da torus (duba Sashe na 8.1.2). Idan muka yi la'akari da tsarin zirga-zirgar ababen hawa tare da layi ɗaya ko ginshiƙi, wanda aka shirya a matsayin zoben ƙusoshi, juyi yana yiwuwa kamar yadda muka gani a Misali na 7. Don guje wa irin waɗannan juyi, bari mu ayyana layukan kwanan wata guda biyu: ɗaya tare da axis na x, da ɗaya tare da axis na y. Layin layi yana haɗar da juyi na kowane ginshiƙi. Waɗannan suna tabbatar da cewa yayin da suke tafiya a cikin torus, juyi na ƙarshe ba zai yiwu ba. Sannan za mu iya amfani da juyi na X-Y azaman tsarin gabaɗaya duk da cewa tare da ƙarin ƙuntatawa cewa lokacin da muka haɗu da layin wecandition to theVCnumbered1. Tare da waɗannan ka'idoji guda biyu, za mu iya tabbatar da cewa juyi a cikin tori ba shi da juyi. VCs tserewa don Maido da Juyi Bari mu kalli wani ra'ayi daban daban. Yi la'akari da misali mai sauƙi tare da VC guda biyu a kowace tashar zahiri. Bari saƙon ya zama an takaita shi zuwa VC 0. Bari mu yi amfani da tsarin hanya mai sauri gajarta don saitin gefuna waɗanda ke amfani da VC 0. Wannan ƙaramin hanyar sadarwa yana ba mu inganci, amma yana iya haifar da rashin nasara. Bari mu gabatar da wata hanya don dawo da makullin kullewa. Ana iya cimma wannan cikin sauƙi ta hanyar haɗa mai ƙidaya da everyflitinarouter. Lokacin da aka shiga, yi amfani da mai ƙidayar. Kowane zagaye yana ƙara mai ƙidayar. Da zarar mai ƙidayar ya bar mai daidaita hanyar sadarwa, muna sake saita mai ƙidayar. Koyaya, idan mai ƙidayar ya kai ga babban ƙofa, to yana nufin cewa makullin ya makale a na'urar na'ura na dogon lokaci. Wannan na iya nuna rashin nasara. Don dalilai na aiki, bari mu ɗauka cewa wannan yana wakiltar yanayin rashin nasara kuma mu yi ƙoƙarin murmurewa daga gare ta. Mayar da makullin kullewa a cikin hanyoyin sadarwa na al'ada ya ƙunshi zubar da fakiti. Koyaya, a yanayin hanyoyin sadarwa na kan-chip, ba a ba da izinin saka fakiti. Saboda haka, muna buƙatar samun wata hanyar da za a iya ɓoyewa daga makullin kullewa. Bari mu sami wani saitin VCs (mai lamba 1). Yi la'akari da ƙaramin hanyar sadarwa da ta ƙunshi VCs mai lamba 1. A cikin wannan ƙaramin hanyar sadarwa, bari mu yi amfani da wata hanyar sadarwa daban wacce ba ta da kullewa kamar hanyar sadarwa ta X-Y. Duk wani juyawa da zai iya makale a cikin kullewa yana komawa zuwa ƙaramin hanyar sadarwa.

tgt_ha: Ba a yi nufin rubuta Smruti R. Sarangi 460 don rubutawa ba. Irin wannan bas ana kiransa bas mai snoopy. Ana kiran ka'idojin daidaita cache waɗanda ke amfani da bas ɗin snoopy da ka'idojin snoopy. Cache 1 Cache 2 Cache 3 Cache 4 Bas Hoto na 9.33: Bas ɗin watsa shirye-shirye Mu za mu tattauna nau'ikan ka'idoji guda biyu na snoopy: rubuta-sabuntawa da rubuta-invalidate. Bari mu bayyana mafi sauƙin ka'idar rubuta-sabuntawa a cikin wannan sashe. Babban ra'ayin shine cewa kowane rubutu ana watsa shi a kan bas ta yadda sauran cache ɗin za su iya ɓoye shi su ɗauki mataki. Kowane cache na 'yar'uwa, C ...C, a cikin cache ɗin da aka rarraba cikakken cache ne a cikin kansa. Zai iya adana kowane toshewa. Zai iya samar da kwafin abin toshewa yana neman. Duk da haka, don tabbatar da cewa waɗannan cache suna bin daidaito, muna buƙatar bin wasu ƙa'idodi. Kafin tsara ƙa'idodi, bari mu fahimci ƙa'idodi. Tunda C ...C galibi cache ne masu zaman kansu, suna iya samun kwafi daban-daban na 1 n guda ɗaya. A wannan yanayin, tabbatar da rubuta serialization (WS) yana da wahala saboda muna iya sabunta kwafi a kowane tsari. Don haka ya zama dole a ƙara ƙuntatawa ga tsarin rubutawa ta yadda ba za a keta axiom na WS ba. Bugu da ƙari, yana yiwuwa saboda akwai bas guda ɗaya, cache na iya samun damar shiga bas akai-akai, kuma saboda haka ba zai iya samun damar zuwa ga wasu cache ba game da buƙatar rubutawa da ya karɓa. Wannan zai karya axiom na yaɗa rubutu (WP). Don haka akwai buƙatar tabbatar da adalci ta yadda ba a keta axiom na WP ba - rubutu a ƙarshe yana bayyane. Karatu Bari mu tsara yarjejeniya mai sauƙi. Duk lokacin da cache ya sami buƙatar karanta, idan akwai bugun karanta, mun tabbata shine ƙimar da ta dace, don haka muna tura ƙimar da sauri ga mai buƙata. Duk da haka, idan akwai kuskuren karanta, to akwai buƙatar fara neman ƙimar da ke cikin sauran cache ɗin 'yar'uwa. Ku tuna cewa a cikin tsarin na gargajiya, da mun aika buƙatar zuwa ƙananan matakin. A wannan yanayin, ba za mu yi hakan ba. Da farko za mu tambayi sauran cache ɗin 'yar'uwa. Sai dai idan duk sun nuna cewa ba su da toshe, to mu kaɗai za mu aika buƙatar zuwa ƙananan matakin. Don aika buƙata ga sauran cache ɗin 'yar'uwa, cache ɗin da ke da kuskuren karanta yana buƙatar fara samun ikon bas ɗin. Da zarar yana da damar shiga bas ɗin ta musamman, yana buƙatar watsa buƙatar kuskuren karanta - wanda aka nuna a matsayin RdX. Muna ɗauka cewa mai kula da bas wanda ke karɓar buƙatu daga cache daban-daban, sannan ya ware musu bas ɗin daidai. Wannan yana tabbatar da cewa yarjejeniyarmu ta bi ƙa'idar WP. Bayan cache ɗin ya watsa saƙon kuskuren karanta, sauran cache ɗin 'yar'uwa suna samun saƙon ta hanyar leƙen asiri a kan bas ɗin. Idan ɗaya daga cikin ma'ajiyar 'yar'uwa tana da kwafin ma'ajiyar, to za ta aika ta bas ɗin zuwa ma'ajiyar da ake buƙata. Akwai wani abu mai sauƙi da ya kamata a yi a nan. A ɗauka cewa ma'ajiyar 'yan'uwa uku suna da kwafin ma'ajiyar. Bai kamata a ce dukkan su ukun su mayar da kwafin ma'ajiyar ba. Wannan ba zai faru a tsarin bas ba, saboda ma'ajiyar da ta fara samun iko a kan bas ɗin za ta aika kwafin ma'ajiyar. Sauran ma'ajiyar za su ga wannan kuma su yanke shawarar kada su aika da amsa (tare da kwafin ma'ajiyar) ga mai buƙata. Bari mu gabatar da wata yarjejeniya mai sauƙi da aka sani da MSI protocol don aiwatar da wannan ra'ayi mai girma. A cikin wannan tsari, kowane ma'ajiyar yana da jihohi uku: modified(M),shared(S),and invalid(I). Tsarin yana biyo baya. Lokacin da aka ba da cacheline babu komai, itissay to beintheinvalidstateI. Lokacin da aka sami kwafin toshewa bayan an gama karantawa, yana canzawa daga yanayin I zuwa yanayinS. S yana nufin yanayin da aka raba, inda aka san cewa ana iya raba toshewar tare da wasu cache. Wannan yana nufin cewa sauran cache na 'yan'uwa na iya samun kwafin toshe iri ɗaya tare da su. Wannan ɓangaren na yarjejeniyar an nuna shi tare da injin jiha.

tgt_ha: Matsayin ɗalibi tsarin} jiha LoggedIn { ... } jiha ViewingGrades { ... } jiha SubmittingAssignment { ... } jiha LoggingOut { ... } jiha InvalidCredentials { ... } A cikin wannan jadawalin jadawalin jiha, ɗan wasan "Ɗalibi" yana canzawa tsakanin jihohi daban-daban bisa ga ayyukansu da kuma amsoshin tsarin . Ga taƙaitaccen bayani game da jihohi da sauye-sauye:  LoggedOut: Yanayin farko lokacin da ɗalibi bai shiga ba. o Idle: Yanayin tsoho lokacin da ɗalibi ya fita kuma yana jiran wani aiki. o LoggingIn: Yanayin lokacin da ɗalibi yake shigar da takardun shaidarsa don shiga.  LoggedIn: Yanayin lokacin da ɗalibi ya yi nasarar shiga.  InvalidCredentials: Yanayin lokacin da ɗalibi ya shigar da takardun shaidar da ba su da inganci yayin <TECH>login. o LoggingOut: Yanayin lokacin da ɗalibi ya fara tsarin fita. o InvalidCredentials: Yanayin lokacin da ɗalibi ya shigar da takardun shaidar da ba su da inganci yayin login.  LoggedIn: Yanayin da ɗalibi ya shiga tsarin <TECH>. o Duba maki: Yanayin da ɗalibi yake kallon makinsa. o SubmittingAssignment: Yanayin da ɗalibi yake gabatar da aiki. o LoggingOut: Yanayin da ɗalibi yake fara tsarin fita. Tsarin jadawalin jiha yana ba da wakilcin gani na jihohi daban-daban da kuma sauye-sauye ga ɗan wasan "Ɗalibi" a cikin tsarin tantance ɗalibai <TECH>. Yana taimakawa wajen fahimtar yanayin da ɗalibi zai iya kasancewa da kuma yadda zai canza tsakanin waɗannan jihohi bisa ga ayyukansu da kuma amsoshin tsarin <TECH>.

tgt_ha: Smruti R. Sarangi 462 Bari mu duba rubuce-rubuce a cikin yanayin M, wanda shine kawai haɗin aikin taron da ba a nuna a Hoto na 9.35 ba. Nan ne muke buƙatar tabbatar da cewa ba a keta ƙa'idar WS (rubuta jerin abubuwa) ba. Bari mu fara la'akari da mafita mai sauƙi wanda zai iya zama mai sauƙin fahimta amma ba daidai ba. Tsarin aikinmu zai iya zama cewa za mu rubuta zuwa toshe, sannan mu watsa rubutun a kan bustowaterestofthesistercachesssuch that they can Sabuntacopy na touch da suke da shi tare da su. Wannan zai tabbatar da cewa a kowane lokaci, duk cache suna da abubuwan da ke cikin touch ɗin iri ɗaya. Duk da haka, wannan ba daidai ba ne. A ɗauka cewa cacheC writes1tox, kuma atthesametimecacheC writes2tox. Sannan za su yi ƙoƙarin watsa ƙimar 1 2. Duk wanda (C ko C) ya sami iko a kan bas ɗin na ƙarshe zai ƙare rubuta ƙimar ƙarshe. A ɗauka cewa watsa shirye-shirye 1 2 C da farko sannan watsa shirye-shiryen C. Yana yiwuwa a kan C karanta karatu biyu a jere za su karanta 1 2 1  waɗannan dabi'u: na farko 1 sannan 2. Yanzu, a kan C za mu iya samun aikin karanta  wanda ya isa 2 bayan mun rubuta 2 zuwa x kawai, kuma ba a yi ko karɓar saƙonnin rubutu a kan bas ɗin ba. A wannan yanayin, za mu  karanta x = 2. Bayan C ta karɓi watsa shirye-shiryen daga C kuma ta sabunta x zuwa 1, aikin  karantawa na biyu akan x ta C zai dawo 1. Don haka, tsarin rubuce-rubucen da C ke fahimta shine (2,1), yayin da ga C shi 2 2 1 shine (1,2). Wannan a bayyane yake ya karya ƙa'idar WS. Rubuce-rubucen ba a jera su ba. Don haka bari mu yi ƙoƙarin gyara wannan. Bari mu yi rubutu atom, inda rubutu zai iya bayyana ga duk cache a lokaci guda. Ana iya yin wannan cikin sauƙi. Lokacin da muke buƙatar rubutawa zuwa wani toshe, wanda yake a cikin cache, muna jira don samun iko akan bus ɗin. Sannan webroadcastthewrite. Allthesisstercaches sabunta kwafin toshe idan suna da kwafin sa. Wannan ya haɗa da cache mai buƙata, wanda ke shafar rubutun lokacin da aka watsa shi cikin nasara. Wannan tsari yana tabbatar da cewa za mu iya aiwatar da aikin rubuta atomic, inda duk cache ɗin ke ganin sa a lokaci guda. Wannan zai tabbatar da rubuta serialization. Hoto na 9.36 yana nuna thefinaldiagramforthetransitionsintheM state. Theflowofactionsonawrite kuskure ne kamar haka: watsa saƙon WrX a kan bas, jira don karɓar kwafin toshe, canzawa zuwa M state, sannan aiwatar da rubutun. Rd | - Wr | Watsa shirye-shirye | WrX I M Evict | Hoto na 9.36: I →M da M →I sun sauya Tillnow, mun duba canjin daga jihar I zuwa jihohin S da M. Muna buƙatar duba canjin tsakanin jihohin SandM. A cikin tsarin sabunta-rubutu, duk da haka muna yin canjin daga jihar M zuwa jihar S. Wannan saboda idan muna da damar rubutu zuwa toshe, to yana nuna cewa muna da damar karanta zuwa toshe. Duk da haka, muna buƙatar yin canji daga jihar S zuwa jihar M idan akwai buƙatar rubutu. Wannan zai nuna cewa mun gyara kwafin toshe. An nuna zane na ƙarshe na yarjejeniyar tare da dukkan jihohi uku a Hoto na 9.37. Canje-canje saboda abubuwan da aka samu daga motar. Akwai nau'ikan abubuwan da ke faruwa guda uku da cache zai iya karɓa daga bas: RdX (karanta kuskure), WrX (rubuta kuskure), da Watsawa (rubutu da ake watsawa zuwa sauran cache). Muna buƙatar aiwatar da waɗannan saƙonnin ga kowanne daga cikin jihohinmu masu inganci: S da M. An nuna zane-zanen canjin yanayi a Hoto na 9.38. Duk lokacin da muka sami kuskuren Karanta ko kuskuren rubutawa daga bas, yana nufin cewa wani ƙaramin cache yana buƙatar a aika masa da kwafin toshe. Ɗaya daga cikin cache ɗin da ke ɗauke da kwafin toshe yana buƙatar amsawa tare da kwafin, kuma lokacin da sauran cache ɗin suka ga amsar ba sa buƙatar aika kwafinsu zuwa cache ɗin neman taimako. Dangane da saƙonni, lokacin da muka karɓi saƙonnin RdX da WrX daga bas ɗin, muna buƙatar fara aiwatar da aika kwafin toshewa ta kan bas ɗin zuwa cache ɗin neman taimako. Wannan yana nuna ta hanyar aikin Aika a Hoto na 9.38. Gaskiyar cewa aikin Aika na iya saboda cache ɗin 'yar'uwa ya riga ya aika kwafin toshewa ba a nuna shi a cikin hoton ba.

tgt_ha: Smruti R. Sarangi 484 yana son rubutawa zuwa toshe a lokaci guda. Saboda mallakarsa ta musamman a cikin yanayin M, toshen yana ci gaba da tsalle tsakanin cache, kuma wannan yana haifar da yawan zirga-zirgar hanyar sadarwa da raguwar aiki. Ana iya rage wannan ta hanyar ƙirƙirar sigar da aka inganta ta makullin juyawa. Bari mu ƙirƙiri kimantawa ta hanyar gwadawa don rubutawa zuwa toshe kawai yana jin cewa akwai yuwuwar babban aikin musayar atomic yana nasara, wanda a madadin haka yana nufin cewa akwai yuwuwar samun makullin. Don cimma wannan, bari mu fara gwada ƙimar makullin ko a'a, kuma idan 0 ne kawai, bari mu yi ƙoƙarin samun makullin. Wannan zai rage yawan saƙonnin da ba su da inganci da adadin lokutan da ake buƙata don amfani da daidaitawa umarni kamar musayar atomic. Lambar aiwatar da wannan ra'ayi kamar haka. 1 /* adireshin makullin yana cikin r0 */ 2 .lock: 3 mov r1, 1 4 5 .test 6 /* gwaji idan makullin shine 0 */ 7 ld r2, 0[r0] 8 cmp r2, 0 9 bne .test 10 11 /* ƙoƙarin musanya kawai idan makullin kyauta ne */ 12 xchg r1, 0[r0] 13 cmp r1, 0 14 bne .test 15 ret 16 17 .unlock: 18 mov r1, 0 19 xchg r1, 0[r0] 20 ret A wannan yanayin, mun ƙara ƙarin layuka uku: Layuka 7 har zuwa 9. Manufar waɗannan layukan shine da farko karanta ƙimar makullin, duba ko daidai yake da 0, sannan ku fita daga madauki idan an gano ƙimar makullin daidai yake da 0. A ɗauka cewa wani zaren ya sami makullin. Sannan zai sami makullin a cikin yanayin M. A karo na farko da zaren na yanzu ya karanta shi, tubalan da ke cikin cache ɗin biyu za su koma yanayin S. Wannan yana buƙatar saƙon kuskure na karanta. Duk da haka, bayan haka zaren na yanzu zai ci gaba da karanta toshe, kuma tunda yana cikin yanayin S, wannan ba zai buƙaci a aika saƙonni zuwa ga directory ba kuma ba ma buƙatar amfani da umarnin musayar atomic don gwada ko makullin kyauta ne ko a'a. Wannan ya fi ƙarfin iko kuma saƙonnin da ke kan NoC za su ragu sosai. Ana kiran wannan hanyar gwaji-da-musayar (HARAJIN). Da zarar mun karanta  ƙimar makullin a matsayin 0, mun tabbata cewa zaren da ke riƙe makullin ya sake shi. Sannan za mu iya ci gaba zuwa Layi na 12, inda muke ƙoƙarin yin musayar atomic. A nan, idan mun yi nasara, to ana ɗaukar mu mun sami makullin. Lura cewa yana yiwuwa zaren biyu na iya sun fahimci cewa kullewar kyauta ce, kuma dukkansu na iya ƙoƙarin aiwatar da aikin musayar atomic a Layi na 12 a lokaci guda. A wannan yanayin, zaren ɗaya ne kawai zai yi nasara. Sauran zaren yana buƙatar fara dukkan aikin ƙoƙarin sake samun kullewar. Gaskiya ne cewa wannan algorithm yana ƙara lokacin da ake buƙata don samun kulle idan babu jayayya. Wannan saboda matakin gwaji na kai. Koyaya, idan yanayin da ake jayayya, za mu buƙaci aiwatar da umarnin musayar abubuwa da yawa ta amfani da algorithms na asali waɗanda muka gabatar. Wannan yana jinkiri saboda aikin shinge na ciki kuma zai haifar da kurakurai da yawa na rubutu. Tare da tsarin TAX, mun maye gurbin kurakurai na rubutu da bugun karanta saboda har sai zaren ya mallaki kullewar, sauran zaren za su ci gaba da karanta canjin kullewar, kuma su same shi a cikin cache ɗinsu a cikin yanayin S: babu saƙonni

tgt_ha: MMH 3.1.3 Sadarwa tsarin (Mai Koyarwa & Malamin Kwas)  Ya kamata a haɗa tsarin aika saƙon tsarin  a cikin CLMS kuma a ba iyaye damar yin magana da malamin ɗansu kai tsaye ta hanyar dandamali.  Wannan fasalin <TECH>ya kamata ya kuma ba iyaye damar ganin saƙonni daga malami ko malami kuma su amsa daidai.  Tsarin aika saƙon ya kamata ya ba iyaye da malami damar raba fayiloli idan ana buƙata. Matakin Fifiko: Babban Sharaɗi: Ba a yarda ba. Nassoshi masu alaƙa: 3.1.4 3.1.4 LR1 - Duba darussa da kayan aiki  Manhajar za ta ta ba wa ɗalibai damar duba darussa da kayan aiki.  Za a ga kwas ɗin ko kayan aikin a cikin jerin.  Za a ga cikakkun bayanai bayani na kwas ɗin da kayan aiki, gami da manufofin koyo, jadawalin kwas, da ƙa'idodin maki.  Jagorar darussa da za a iya bincikawa da za a bayar Matakin Fifiko: Babban Sharaɗi: Ɗalibi zai ga jerin idan kuma kawai yana da asusun da aka yi rijista kuma ya shiga cikin wannan asusun. Nassoshi Masu Alaƙa: N/A 3.1.5 LR2 - Zaɓi darussa da kayan aiki  Manhajar za ta za ta ba wa ɗalibai damar zaɓar darussa da kayan aiki.  CLMS za ta nuna jadawalin kwas ɗin, gami da ranakun farawa da ƙarewa, tsawon lokacin kwas ɗin, da duk wani muhimmin ranaku ko wa'adin ƙarshe.  Idan darussa ba kyauta ba ne, CLMS ya kamata ta bayar da tsarin biyan kuɗi tsarin don gudanar da ma'amaloli cikin aminci.  CLMS ya kamata ta samar da takardar shaida ko alamar dijital bayan kammala kwas, wanda ɗalibai za su iya rabawa akan bayanan ci gaba ko bayanan kafofin watsa labarun. tgt_ha: Bukatun ManhajaTakamaiman Bayani ga Mataimakin Ɗalibi Shafi na 28 Ana aiwatar da daidaitawa tare da ayyuka na waje, bayanai, ko ajiyar girgije ta hanyar ingantattun hanyoyin daidaitawa don tabbatar da daidaiton Bayanai a tsakanin na'urori da dandamali.  Tsarin Saƙo: Saƙonni da Bayanai da aka yi musayar su sun dace da tsarin daidai Bayanai da tsare-tsare don ba da damar haɗa kai ba tare da matsala ba tare da tsarin waje da ayyuka.  Ka'idojin Sadarwa: Aikace-aikacen  yana bin ƙa'idodin sadarwa da aka yarda da su sosai, kamar HTTP, HTTPS, da OAuth2, yana tabbatar da daidaito da haɗin kai tare da tsarin waje da ayyuka.  Sadarwa ta Ainihin Lokaci: Siffofin sadarwa na ainihin lokaci, kamar hulɗar hira da mataimakin AI na kama-da-wane, sun haɗa da musayar Bayanai nan take tare da ƙarancin lattin . Mataimakin Ɗalibi ya fi mai da hankali kan sadarwa mai aminci da inganci, yana amfani da ɓoye bayanai, ƙa'idodi na yau da kullun, da hanyoyin daidaitawa don sauƙaƙe hulɗa mai inganci da amsawa tare da tsarin da ayyuka na waje.

Saboda haka, yawan jama'a ana bayyana shi a matsayin adadin mutane a kowace murabba'in kilomita. A bisa ga ƙidayar jama'a ta 2001, yawan jama'a a Indiya shine mutane 324 a kowace murabba'in kilomita. A cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata yawan jama'a ya ƙaru fiye da sau huɗu. Ya ƙaru daga 77 a 1901 zuwa 324 a 2001. Idan muka ce yawan jama'ar Indiya shine mutane 324 a kowace murabba'in kilomita, wannan ba yana nufin cewa yawan jama'a shine daidai mutane 324 a kowace murabba'in kilomita ba. Bayani Hoto na 26.1: INDIA: Rarraba Yawan Jama'a 2001 A zahiri, rarraba yawan jama'a a Indiya ba shi da daidaito sosai. Rashin daidaiton yawan jama'a a Indiya ya bayyana a fili cewa a Arunachal Pradesh matsakaicin adadin jama'a mutum 13 ne kawai a kowace murabba'in kilomita, yayin da mutane 9,294 ne a kowace murabba'in kilomita a Delhi kamar yadda aka kiyasta a shekarar 2001. tgt_ha: 113 Smruti R. Sarangi Matsalar da muke son magancewa a wannan sashe ita ce ƙirƙirar wata hanyar da za ta bi diddigin da warware dogaro tsakanin umarni. Dole ne a sami wata hanyar da umarnin mai samarwa zai iya sanar da duk umarnin mai amfani da shi cewa ƙimar rajistar wurin da za ta je ta shirya. Ainihin yana buƙatar watsa ƙimar da aka samar zuwa ga umarnin cin abinci. Bugu da ƙari, don wannan tsarin ya yi aiki, kowane umarnin mai amfani yana buƙatar jira operand ɗinsa su shirya. Da zarar duk operand ɗinsa sun shirya, ana cewa farkawa 1 Bari mu gabatar da tsarin tsarin watsa shirye-shirye da farkawa, inda mai samarwa ke watsa bayanai game da kammala shi, kuma umarnin mai amfani yana amfani da wannan bayanai don farkawa. Za mu fara tattauna tsarin watsa shirye-shirye (duba Hoto na 4.15). Alamar bus rs1 shirye1 rs2 shirye2 Alamar bus Hoto na 4.15: Tagar umarni tare da ƙarin dabaru don watsawa da kwatantawa Alamar kowane shigarwa a cikin taga umarni an haɗa shi da aƙalla saitin wayoyi na tagulla guda ɗaya da ake kira alamar bus. Ana amfani da alamar bus don watsa lambar rajista ta zahiri wacce aka rubuta ƙimarta zuwa fayil ɗin rajista. A madadin haka, muna kiran wannan lambar a matsayin alamar. Umarnin mai samarwa yana watsa alamarsa (id na rajistar wurin da za ta je) akan motar tag: wannan an haɗa shi da duka ayyukan tushen 1 da 2. Idan muna da umarni da yawa da ke gudana a kowane zagaye, to muna buƙatar motocin tag da yawa. Umarni yana rubuta lambar rajistar wurin da za ta je zuwa motar tag ɗin da ta dace. Hoto na 4.15 yana nuna motocin tag guda biyu: ɗaya ga kowane umarnin mai samarwa. Bari mu yi bayani dalla-dalla. Yi la'akari da ɗan ƙaramin lambar da ke ƙasa. 1 ƙara r1, r2, r3 2 ƙara r4, r1, r5 Umarni na 1 shine umarnin mai samarwa. Yana samar da ƙimar rajistar r1. A ɗauka cewa an tsara rajistar r1 zuwa rajistar jiki p17. Sannan 17 shine ƙimar alamar da ake watsawa a kan motar tag ɗin da ta dace. Kowace shigarwa a cikin taga umarnin an haɗa ta da duk motocin tag. Ga kowane operand na tushe, muna duba don gano ko daidai yake da kowane alamar da aka watsa. Ana yin wannan tare da taimakon masu kwatantawa da ƙofar OR kamar yadda aka nuna a Hoto na 4.15. Idan akwai daidaito, to za mu san cewa operand ɗin tushen da ya dace ya shirya. tgt_ha: BABI NA 4. CONCLAMURKAIONS 30 4.2 Hasashen Ayyukanmu na Gaba Idan muka yi la'akari da gaba, hasashe na gaba ga Econscious suna da ban mamaki, yayin da aikinmu ke ci gaba da haɓaka da faɗaɗa tasirinsa akan rayuwa mai ɗorewa da kiyaye muhalli. Yayin da muke ƙoƙarin ƙara haɗa fasahohin zamani da mafita masu ƙirƙira a cikin dandamalinmu, muna tsammanin ƙarin shiga da shiga daga mutane, al'ummomi, da ƙwararru. Ta hanyar amfani da nazarin bayanai da algorithms na koyon injina, don haɓaka tasiri da ingancin hanyoyin sarrafa sharar gida, inganta amfani da albarkatu da rage matsin lamba na muhalli. Bugu da ƙari, muna hasashen ƙirƙirar haɗin gwiwa mai mahimmanci tare da hukumomin gwamnati, ƙungiyoyin NGO, da ƙungiyoyin kamfanoni don haɓaka isa da tasirinmu, haɓaka hanyar sadarwa ta duniya ta zakarun dorewa waɗanda suka himmatu wajen gina duniya mai kore da juriya. Bugu da ƙari, yayin da wayar da kan jama'a da buƙatar ayyukan kyautata muhalli ke ci gaba da ƙaruwa, ana sa ran ci gaban amfani da kuma haɗin gwiwar al'umma, wanda ke ƙarfafa matsayin Econscious a matsayin jagora a cikin motsi mai dorewa na rayuwa. Tare da sadaukarwa mai ƙarfi da jajircewa ga manufarmu, muna da tabbacin cewa Econscious zai taka rawar gani a cikin siffantawa, mafi dorewar makoma ga tsararraki masu zuwa.

tgt_ha: Yin Rajista a Wurin Wasanni Tsarin Kirtan Shah I Bayanin Aikin 1 Bayanin Aikin 1a Takaitaccen Bayani Akan Aikin Wannan aikace-aikacen  an tsara shi ne don sauƙaƙe tsarin gano, yin rajista da kuma kula da wuraren wasanni, biyan buƙatun manajojin wurare, 'yan wasa da masu sha'awar wasanni. Aikace-aikacen  yana ba da mafita mai sauƙi ga masu amfani da  don bincika da shiga cikin zaɓin wasanni a wurin wasanni da ake da su, kwatanta farashi da kayan more rayuwa da kuma yin rajista a ainihin lokaci. Yana ba da dandamali ga wasanni da yawa kamar wasan kurket, ƙwallon ƙafa, wasan tennis, golf, ƙwallon pickle da ƙari. Dandalin kuma yana ba masu kula da wuraren damar sarrafawa da inganta rajista yadda ya kamata da kuma sa ido kan amfani da kuɗaɗen shiga waɗanda ke taimakawa wajen haɓaka riba. 1b Bayanin Aikin Wannan aikin yana game da sauƙaƙa wa mutane su nemo, yin rajista, da kuma sarrafa wuraren wasanni, ko kai manajan wurare ne, ɗan wasa, ko kuma kawai mai sha'awar wasanni. Manufar ita ce a kawo komai cikin manhaja ɗaya mai sauƙin amfani, inda masu amfani za su iya bincika da yin rajistar wurare don wasanni kamar wasan kurket, ƙwallon ƙafa, wasan tennis, wasan golf, ƙwallon pickle, da ƙari, duk a ainihin lokaci. Maimakon yin tsalle daga gidan yanar gizo zuwa gidan yanar gizo, masu amfani za su iya kwatanta farashi, duba kayan more rayuwa, da kuma tabbatar da wurinsu kai tsaye daga wayarsu ko kwamfutarsu. Ga masu kula da kayan aiki, manhajar tana ba da kayan aiki don taimakawa wajen sauƙaƙe ayyukansu - ko dai inganta yin rajista, bin diddigin amfani, ko haɓaka kudaden shiga. Manajoji za su iya sarrafa bayanan wurin aikinsu, <TECH>sabunta abin da ke akwai, ci gaba da bin diddigin yin rajista a ainihin lokaci, har ma da duba jadawalin yin rajista. Hakanan yana taimaka musu su kula da biyan kuɗi da kuma samar da rahotanni kan aikin <TECH> na wurin aikinsu. Babban abin da ke haifar da wannan aikin shine magance matsalolin da ake fuskanta tare da yin rajistar wuraren wasanni. A yanzu, mutane sau da yawa suna fuskantar wahalar kira ko ziyartar gidajen yanar gizo da yawa don nemo wurin da ake da shi. Wannan manhajar tana haɗa komai, wanda hakan ke sa ya zama mai sauƙi da sauri ga masu amfani su gano, kwatantawa, da yin rajistar kayan aiki. Bugu da ƙari, 1

tgt_ha: MASU KYAU - 9 Ci gaban Dan Adam Ci gaban albarkatun ɗan adam a Indiya matsakaici ne Uttar Pradesh, Bihar, Andhra Pradesh, Assam, Haryana, Punjab, Jammu da Kashmir, Jharkhand da Nagaland. Domin inganta samun ilimi, musamman rajista da riƙewa a matakin farko da rage jahilci na manya. Gwamnatin Indiya ta fara sabbin shirye-shirye daban-daban kuma ta ƙarfafa shirye-shiryen da ake da su. Alamomin Tattalin Arziki Bayanan kula Ci gaban ɗan adam ya kuma sanya babban mahimmanci ga yawan aiki da ci gaban tattalin arziki. Wannan yana ba da damar ci gaba ban da ilimi da lafiya. Ana gano ci gaban tattalin arziki gabaɗaya tare da Jimlar Kayayyakin Cikin Gida (GDP), Jimlar Kayayyakin Ƙasa (GNP), kuɗin shiga ga kowane mutum, da sauransu. A nan ba za mu tattauna dalla-dalla duk waɗannan alamun tattalin arziki da aka ambata a sama ba, amma za mu tattauna ne kawai game da kuɗin shiga ga kowane mutum. A cewar Binciken Tattalin Arziki na 2005-06, kuɗin shiga ga kowane mutum ya ƙaru daga Rs 3,687 a 1950-51 zuwa Rs 19,649 a 2004-05. Kodayake kuɗin shiga ga kowane mutum ya ƙaru sosai amma bambance-bambancen suna da faɗi sosai a matakin yanki da na gida. Ko a yankunan karkara da birane, akwai babban bambanci a cikin kudin shiga na kowane mutum. Irin wannan bambancin kuma ana nuna shi ta hanyar mutanen da ke ƙasa da layin talauci. Talauci ba wai kawai wani lamari ne na tattalin arziki ba, har ma da rashin walwala a zamantakewa da tunani. Wannan yana bayyana ta hanyar rashin ingancin rayuwa, rashin abinci mai gina jiki, ƙarancin ci gaban ɗan adam, da sauransu. A cewar kiyasin Hukumar Tsare-tsare a cikin 1999-2000, akwai kashi 26.10% na yawan jama'a da ke zaune a ƙasa da layin talauci. Wannan rabon shine kashi 27.09% a yankunan karkara da kashi 23.62% a yankunan birane. Duk da cewa talaucin karkara yana da alaƙa da manoma marasa filaye da marasa galihu, talaucin birni yana bayyana ta fuskar yaɗuwar ƙauyuka a birane. Jihohin da yawan jama'a ke ƙasa da layin talauci daga matsakaicin ƙasa sun haɗa da Orissa, Bihar (gami da Jharkhand), Madhya Pradesh (gami da Chhatisgarh), Uttar Pradesh (gami da Uttarakhand), duk jihohin arewa maso gabas ban da Mizoram da West Bengal. tgt_ha: Smruti R. Sarangi 616 Ma'anar Kalma Ma'anar Kalma µ Motsi na sifili C Ƙarfin oxide na ƙofar 0 ox W Faɗi L Tsawon m Ƙarfin juyawa na ƙasa v kT/q T V Ƙarfin ƙofa V Ƙarfin shiga ƙarfin lantarki g th V Ƙarfin tushen magudanar ruwa k Ƙarfin Boltzmann na yau da kullun DS q 1.6×10−19 C T Zafin jiki (a cikin Kelvins) Ɗaya daga cikin mahimman kalmomi a cikin wannan lissafi shine v = kT/q, wanda aka sani da ƙarfin T na thermal wanda ya yi daidai da zafin jiki. Mun ga cewa I yana daidai da murabba'in vds T ta hanyar kalmar v2, kuma yana dogara sosai akan shi ta hanyar sharuɗɗan biyu waɗanda ke da v a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙimar T T. Saboda waɗannan alaƙar, na dogon lokaci an ɗauka cewa kwararar ruwa aikin ƙima ne na zafin jiki. Duk da haka, wannan dangantakar ba gaskiya ba ce ta 2020. Sultan et al. [Sultan et al., 2018] a cikin bincikensu sun nuna cewa a mafi yawan lokuta samfurin layi na zubar da ruwa daidai ne (cikin 6%) a cikin kewayon zafin jiki 40◦C-80◦C. Wannan saboda Daidaito 11.9 kusan layi ne a cikin wannan kewayon zafin jiki. Don ƙarin daidaito, yana da kyau a yi amfani da samfurin layi na yanki ko samfurin kwata-kwata. Kurakurai ga duka samfuran suna cikin 1%. A cikin na'urori masu gajeriyar hanya, yankuna na tushe da magudanar ruwa suna kusa da juna. Sakamakon haka, ƙarfin babban TECH> na transistor ya dogara da ƙarfin lantarki na tushen magudanar ruwa, V. Wannan tasirin DS ana kiransa da rage shingen da aka haifar da magudanar ruwa (DIBL). Yayin da V ke ƙaruwa, yana rage ƙarfin <TECH>babban TECH>, DS wanda ke ƙara ƙara ƙarfin zubar da ruwa na ƙasa kamar yadda aka tsara a cikin Daidaito 11.9. Wutar zubar da ruwa ta ƙasa kuma ta dogara da jiki zuwa ƙarfin lantarki (biyayya ga jiki). Idan aka juya aka juya, to ƙarfin <TECH>matsakaici yana ƙaruwa, kuma wannan yana rage kwararar kwarara. Haka nan, idan muka ci gaba da wannan mahadar, to ƙarfin matsakaici yana raguwa - transistor yana yin sauri akan farashin kwararar kwarara mafi girma. Daidaiton alaƙar da ke tsakanin ƙarfin matsakaici da kuma ƙarfin jiki ya dogara ne akan fasahar transistor. Yawancin kayan aikin kwaikwayo na kewaye ciki har da Spice na iya yin kwaikwayon son zuciya na jiki. Son zuciya wata hanya ce mai mahimmanci don daidaita yawan amfani da wutar lantarki a cikin da'irori. I: Tunneling Gate Oxide 3 Tare da ƙaruwar ƙarancin aiki, kauri na oxide na ƙofar yana raguwa, kuma wannan yana ƙara filin lantarki a fadin oxide na ƙofar. Wannan yana haifar da tasirin injiniya na quantum da aka sani da tunneling. A nan, electrons (ko ramuka) a cikin tashar na iya tserewa kai tsaye zuwa oxide na ƙofar ko ƙofar. Duk wani kwararar electrons (ko ramuka) yana da alaƙa da halin yanzu. A wannan yanayin, hasken leaking ne saboda a cikin transistor mai kyau ana ɗaukar oxide na ƙofar a matsayin cikakken insulator. Akwai hanyoyi guda biyu don magudanar ruwa ta gate oxide: Magudanar ruwa ta Fowler-Nordheim da kuma sarrafa kai tsaye. A cikin magudanar ruwa ta Fowler-Nordheim, ana motsa lantarki zuwa magudanar ruwa ta layin oxide saboda filin lantarki na waje. Lura cewa a cikin magudanar ruwa, electrons suna da motsi mai mahimmanci kuma ana iya amfani da su don gudanar da wutar lantarki. Sauran hanyoyin ana kiransu magudanar ruwa kai tsaye, wanda ke ƙara zama ruwan dare yayin da kauri girman oxide na ƙofar ke raguwa zuwa 'yan nanometers (< 3-4 nm). A wannan yanayin, electrons da ramuka suna ratsa kai tsaye daga saman magudanar ruwa ta silicon zuwa ƙofar (yawanci ana yin su da polysilicon). I: Allurar Mai ɗaukar zafi 4 Wannan yayi kama da Magudanar Ruwa ta Gate Oxide dangane da gaskiyar cewa a nan ma electrons ko ramuka suna tserewa ta hanyar Si-SiO2 (silicon da gate oxide). Duk da haka, tsarin ya bambanta. Saboda 2 daga cikin manyan filayen lantarki, wasu electrons suna samun isasshen kuzarin motsi (suna zama masu ɗaukar zafi) don ketare hanyar haɗin gwiwa da motsawa daga substrate zuwa ƙofar (idan akwai ƙofar da aka caji da kyau). A Babi na 12, za mu yi nazarin tasirin irin waɗannan masu ɗaukar zafi akan amincin ƙofar, kuma mu fahimci yadda allurar mai ɗaukar zafi ke haifar da rushewar oxide na ƙofar a hankali. Wannan lamari yana da alaƙa da tsufan transistor inda sigogin transistor ke canzawa a hankali akan lokaci.

Jerin 14.1: 2D Convolution don (n=0; n<N; n++) { /* hotunan shigarwa */ don (k=0; k<K; k++) { /* fitarwa */ don (c=0; c<C; c++) { /* tashoshin shigarwa */ don (h=0; h<H; h++) { /* layuka na ifmap/ofmap */ don (w=0; w<W; w++) { /* cols na ifmap/ofmap */ don (r=0; r<R; r++) { /* layuka na matattarar */ don (s=0; s<S; s++){ /* cols na matattarar */ O[n][k][h][w] += I[n][c][h+r][w+s] * F[k][c][r][s]; }}}}}}} Lambar da ke cikin Jerin 14.1 tana da wasu muhimman fasaloli, waɗanda sune kamar haka. 1. Tsarin madaukai ba shi da mahimmanci. Tunda akwai dogaro tsakanin madaukai masu canzawa, za mu iya sake tsara madaukai ta kowace hanya da muke so. Za mu ga cewa wannan yana da mahimmanci idan aka zo ga wurin cache. 2. Ga kowane pixel na fitarwa, muna yin ninkawa na C × R × S da adadin ƙari iri ɗaya. Don haka muna yin jimlar ayyukan 2C × R × S. Yawancin ISA suna ba da aikin ninkawa da tarawa (MAC) wanda ke yin lissafin siffar a += b × c kama da abin da muke yi. Yawan ayyuka a cikin suchalgorithm yawanci ana ambaton su a cikin temsoft adadin ayyukan MAC. Mun lura cewa yin fitarwa pixel yana aiwatar da C × R × S MACa'idodin inda muke ƙara jimlar ɓangare zuwa pixel na fitarwa (wanda aka fara zuwa 0). A nan, ana kiran samfurin I[n][c][h+ r][w+s]×F[k][c][s] a matsayin jimlar ɓangare. 3. A zahiri muna bayyana sarari mai girma 7 inda girman yake da kansa. Wannan sarari za a iya rage shi - ya lalace zuwa ƙananan sarari. Bari mu bayyana misali. A ɗauka cewa mun canza ƙaruwar madaukai masu maimaitawa w da h daga 1 zuwa 3. Yana nufin muna la'akari da tayal 3 × 3 na pixels na fitarwa. Sannan muna buƙatar ƙara madaukai biyu na ciki waɗanda ke ratsa kowane tayal (sarari 3 × 3) kuma mu ƙididdige jimillar ɓangarorin da suka dace kuma mu ƙara su don samun taswirar. 4. Ganin cewa lissafin suna da zaman kansu, muna da babbar dama don gudanar da wannan lambar akan saitin masu sarrafawa masu kama da juna, inda kowane tsari an ba shi adadin aiki. Wannan kuma ya dace da ra'ayinmu na madauki yayin da ƙaramin adadin aiki za a iya ba wa kowane mai sarrafawa. Bugu da ƙari, tunda waɗannan masu sarrafawa dole ne kawai su yi ayyukan MAC da maimaitawa ta hanyar madauki, ba ma buƙatar masu sarrafawa na yau da kullun. Kamar GPU, za mu iya ƙirƙirar jerin ƙananan masu sarrafawa masu sauƙi. Bari mu kira irin wannan ƙaramin mai sarrafawa mai sauƙi a matsayin abin sarrafawa ko PE.

tgt_ha: Smruti R. Sarangi yana da ragowa 276. Ko da a zahiri muna buƙatar ragowa 19 a wannan yanayin, har yanzu muna amfani da ragowa 20 muna tuna cewa za mu iya ƙara ƙarin ƙwaƙwalwar jiki ko musanya sarari daga baya, koda a lokacin aiki. Wannan ra'ayi ne na daidaitacce wanda aka yi a cikin duk tsarin aiki. Idan ba a yi amfani da wasu ragowa na MSB ba, ana iya saita su zuwa 0. Saboda haka, a taƙaice, tsarin taswirarmu yana buƙatar canza lambar shafi ta 20-bit zuwa lambar firam ta 20-bit. Muna buƙatar kula da tsarin Bayanai a cikin software don adana irin waɗannan taswira don kowane tsari. Irin wannan tsarin Bayanai ana kiransa teburin shafi. Akwai hanyoyi daban-daban na aiwatar da teburin shafi yadda ya kamata. Mai karatu zai iya komawa zuwa littattafai kan tsarin aiki [Silberschatz et al., 2018] ko rubutun baya na Sarangi [Sarangi, 2015] don tattaunawa mai zurfi akan teburin shafi. Hanya mara hankali ita ce a sami teburin shafi guda ɗaya mai matakai 220, inda kowane shigarwa ke adana id na firam: rago 20. Jimlar sarari buƙatar shine 2.5 MB a kowane tsari, wanda hakan haramun ne. Don adana sarari, yawancin teburin shafi an tsara su azaman tebura masu matakai 2, inda muke amfani da manyan rago 10 don samun damar a matsayin teburin shafi na farko. Kowane shigarwa na teburin shafi na farko yana nuna zuwa teburin shafi na biyu. Muna amfani da rago 10 na gaba na id ɗin shafi don samun damar teburin shafi na biyu wanda ke ɗauke da taswirar. Lura cewa duk abubuwan da ke cikin teburin shafi na farko ba za su nuna a matsayin teburin shafi na biyu ba. Wannan saboda yawancin shigarwar za su yi daidai da sassan sararin adireshin da ba a amfani da su ba. Sakamakon haka, za mu iya adana sarari mai yawa ta hanyar ƙirƙirar waɗancan teburin shafi na biyu kawai da ake buƙata. Don sararin adireshin bit 64 za mu iya tsara a matsayin teburin shafi na mataki 3 ko mataki 4. Akwai waɗanda aka gayyata don yin nazarin buƙatun sarari na tebura daban-daban na shafi; Tana buƙatar ta shawo kan kanta cewa samun teburin shafi mai matakai da yawa kyakkyawan ra'ayi ne ga manyan wuraren adireshi na kama-da-wane. Abin baƙin ciki, tare da irin waɗannan teburin shafi muna buƙatar samun dama da yawa zuwa tsarin ƙwaƙwalwar  don karanta shigarwa ɗaya. Wasu daga cikin waɗannan shigarwar wataƙila suna cikin cache; duk da haka, a cikin mafi munin yanayi muna iya buƙatar samun dama da yawa zuwa babban ƙwaƙwalwar ajiya. Ganin cewa kowace babbar hanyar samun damar ƙwaƙwalwa tana ɗaukar kusan zagaye 200 zuwa 400 dangane da fasahar, wannan aiki ne mai tsada sosai. Yanzu idan muka kalli waɗannan lambobi bisa ga gaskiyar cewa muna buƙatar yin taswirar kama-da-wane don kowane damar samun ƙwaƙwalwar ajiya, ana sa ran aikin  zai zama mara kyau sosai. A bayyane yake ba za mu iya biyan irin waɗannan ayyuka masu tsada ga kowane damar samun ƙwaƙwalwar ajiya ba. Wannan zai rage duk ribar da muka samu wajen ƙirƙirar bututun da ba a tsara shi ba da kuma tsarin ƙwaƙwalwar ajiya mai ci gaba <TECH>. Abin godiya, akwai mafita mai sauƙi. Za mu iya amfani da ra'ayoyin da muka yi amfani da su wajen adana bayanai: locality da spacelocality. Muna ajiye ƙananan kayan aiki na kwamfuta waɗanda aka sani da TranslationLookasideBuffer (TLB) tare da kowane ma'auni. Wannan yana riƙe da taswirar da aka yi amfani da su kwanan nan daga shafukan yanar gizo na kama-da-wane zuwa lambobin firam na jiki. Idan aka yi la'akari da kadarorin wurin zama na ɗan lokaci, muna tsammanin samun babban adadin bugawa a cikin TLB. Wannan saboda yawancin shirye-shirye suna son samun damar shiga saitin shafuka iri ɗaya akai-akai. Bugu da ƙari, za mu iya amfani da wurin zama na sarari. Tunda yawancin hanyoyin shiga za su kasance zuwa ga adiresoshin da ke kusa, ana sa ran su kasance cikin shafi ɗaya. Saboda haka, ana sa ran adana taswirar a matakin shafuka zai zama da amfani sosai saboda yana da yuwuwar sake amfani da shi sosai. Ma'ana 45 • Teburin shafi tsari ne na <TECH>data wanda ke kula da taswirar tsakanin lambobin shafi da lambobin firam ɗin da suka dace. A mafi yawan lokuta wannan tsarin Bayanai ana kiyaye shi a cikin yankin ƙwaƙwalwar ajiya ta software. Modules na musamman na tsarin  mai aiki suna kula da teburin shafi daban don kowane tsari. Duk da haka, a cikin wasu gine-gine, musamman sabbin na'urori masu sarrafa bayanai, tsarin neman taswirar (wanda kuma ake kira tafiya ta shafi) ana yin sa ne ta hanyar kayan aiki. • Don rage yawan kuɗin fassarar adireshi, muna amfani da ƙaramin ma'ajiyar taswirar tsakanin shafuka da firam. Wannan ana kiransa da Translate Lookaside Buffer ko TLB. Yawanci yana ɗauke da shigarwa 32-128, kuma ana iya samun damar shiga ba tare da zagayowar agogo 1 ba. Yana da mahimmanci don samun damar shiga TLB duk lokacin da muka bayar da buƙatar kaya/shago zuwa tsarin <TECH>.

tgt_ha: 1. Gabatarwa 1.1. Manufa Manufar wannan takardar Bayanin Bukatun Software (SRS) ita ce a fayyace buƙatun AI-Powered Health and Fitness Tracker, aikace-aikacen Android  wanda aka tsara don sauƙaƙe kula da lafiya da motsa jiki. Takardar tana yi wa masu haɓakawa, masu kula da ayyuka, masu ruwa da tsaki, da masu gwaji hidima, suna tabbatar da fahimtar manufofin Tsarin. Aikace-aikacen  yana amfani da AI don bin diddigin abinci da motsa jiki ta atomatik, yana rage shigar da hannu, kuma yana haɗa gamification don haɓaka haɗin gwiwar mai amfani. 1.2. Faɗin AI-Powered Health and Fitness Tracker aikace-aikacen wayar hannu ne na  wanda ke niyya ga masu sha'awar motsa jiki da mutanen da ke da masaniyar lafiya. Manyan fasaloli sun haɗa da:  Shawarwarin abinci mai amfani da AI bisa ga abinci da manufofin motsa jiki.  Gano abinci ta amfani da samfuran AI bisa hoto.  Shirye-shiryen motsa jiki na musamman waɗanda AI ke jagoranta.  Bin diddigin shan ruwa mai wayo tare da tunatarwa.  Bin diddigin ci gaba tare da fahimtar lafiya bisa AI.  Siffofin Gamification (launuka, alamomi, lada).  Tantance Mai amfani da daidaitawa Bayanai. An gina tsarin  ta amfani da Jetpack Compose don frontend, Firebase Firestore don backend, da samfuran AI kamar Food101, Llama, da Facebook Prophet. Abubuwan da aka keɓe sun haɗa da gano matsayi na ainihi, haɗakar da aka sawa, da kuma koyarwa kai tsaye, waɗanda aka tsara don sabuntawa na gaba. Takaddun sun haɗa da dogaro da haɗin intanet da damar kyamarar na'ura. 1.3. Ma'anoni, Kalmomi masu kama da juna, da gajerun kalmomi o AI: Ƙwaƙwalwar wucin gadi, da ake amfani da ita don shawarwarin abinci da motsa jiki. o BMI: Ma'aunin Jiki na Jiki, ma'aunin kitsen jiki. o API: Aikace-aikacen Tsarin Shirye-shirye, don Bayanai da haɗin AI. o GUI: Tsarin Zane na Mai amfani, don hulɗar mai amfani</TECH>. o DBMS: Bayanan Bayanai Gudanarwa Tsarin, don ajiyar bayanai. o UX: Mai amfani Kwarewa, babban app ɗin amfani. o NLP: Sarrafa Harshe na Halitta, wanda aka yi amfani da shi a cikin samfuran AI. 1.4. Nassoshi  IEEE Std 830-1998: Shawarar IEEE don Ayyukan Bukatun Software.  Rufe Fuska Abinci101 Takardun Samfura.  Takardun Samfura na LLAMA.  Takardun Annabi na Facebook.  Edamam Nutrition API Takardun.  Takardun Shagon Wuta na Firebase.

tgt_ha: 761 Smruti R. Sarangi Snapdragon 865 yana ba da damar yin aiki na tiriliyan 15 na AI a kowace daƙiƙa. Qualcomm yana da na'urar sarrafa siginar hoto (ISP) a cikin guntu don sarrafa hotunan da kyamarori suka ɗauka. Yana iya sarrafa biliyoyin pixels a kowace daƙiƙa. Wannan yawanci yana da mahimmanci don samar da wuraren mayar da hankali kai tsaye, yin zuƙowa na gani, ɗaukar hotuna da bidiyo marasa motsi, da kuma ɗaukar bidiyon motsi mai jinkiri. Tun daga shekarar 2020, muna shiga zamanin 5G. 5G a ƙa'ida zai iya tallafawa mafi girman ƙimar Bayanai na 10 Gbps. Yawancin tsarin 5G ana sa ran za su yi amfani da raƙuman milimita don aika Bayanai a cikin mita mai yawa. Tun daga tsakiyar 2020, akwai iyaka ga tura 5G a duniya; duk da haka, fasahar tana nuna alƙawari mai yawa. Saboda haka, masu kera chip na wayar hannu suna buƙatar tabbatar da cewa SoCs ɗinsu suna shirye don 5G. Qualcomm ya ƙara modem X55 5G a cikin motherboard napdragon (lura cewa guntu ne daban). Tare da haka, Qualcommya kuma haɗa wasu kwakwalwan kwamfuta tare da na'urar sarrafawa ta Snapdragon a kan motherboard, wanda ya haɗa da kwakwalwan mara waya mai sauri da Bluetooth. Yayin da suke tsara babban SoC, masu ƙira galibi suna fuskantar matsala: ya kamata su sami wasu sassa a cikin SoC ko kuma su sanya su a waje da shi a kan motherboard? Tsohon shawarar ƙira zai iya samar mana da babban aikin <TECH>muddin za mu iya tabbatar da cewa za mu iya ƙirƙirar irin wannan babban guntu tare da ƙimar yawan aiki mai karɓuwa, kuma mu ci gaba da watsa wutar lantarki a kan guntu a ƙasa da wani takamaiman matakin <TECH>. Idan yawan amfani da wutar lantarki matsala ce ko kuma akwai yiwuwar guntu ya yi girma sosai kuma ƙimar yawan amfanin ƙasa za ta ragu, ana iya ƙera sassan kuma a sanya su a kusa da allon uwa.

tgt_ha: Smruti R. Sarangi 270 Victim Cache Ma'ajiyar wanda aka azabtar ƙaramin cache ne wanda yawanci ake ƙarawa tsakanin cache na L1 da L2. Abin lura shi ne cewa wani lokacin muna da wasu saiti a cikin cache na L1 waɗanda ke ganin adadin shiga mara kyau, don haka muna samun kurakurai. Misali, a cikin cache mai haɗin kai mai hanyoyi 4, muna iya samun tubalan guda 5 da ake amfani da su akai-akai waɗanda ke nuna saitin iri ɗaya. A wannan yanayin, ɗayan tubalan za a fitar da su daga cache akai-akai. Maimakon zuwa matakin ƙasa, wanda aiki ne mai jinkiri, za mu iya ƙara ƙaramin cache tsakanin L1 da L2 wanda ke ɗauke da irin waɗannan tubalan waɗanda aka azabtar. Yana iya samun shigarwa 8-64 wanda hakan zai sa ya zama ƙanana kuma mai sauri. Ga shirye-shirye da yawa, cache waɗanda aka azabtar suna da matuƙar amfani duk da ƙaramin girmansu. Sau da yawa yana da mahimmanci a zaɓi waɗanda tubalan da ake buƙatar ƙarawa a cikin cache na wanda aka azabtar. Ba za mu so mu ƙara tubalan da ke da ƙarancin yuwuwar samun damar shiga nan gaba ba. Za mu iya bin diddigin amfani da saitin tare da ƙirgawa kuma mu adana tubalan da aka kora kawai na waɗannan saitin da ake yawan shiga. Rage Hukuncin Miss Rage hukuncin kuskure daidai yake da rage lokacin samun damar ƙwaƙwalwa a matakin ƙasa. Wannan ya haɗa da rage lokacin bugawa ko ƙimar kuskure a matakin ƙasa. Duk da haka, akwai tsare-tsare waɗanda aka tsara musamman don rage hukuncin kuskure. Ɗaya daga cikin irin wannan tsarin shine kalma mai mahimmanci da farawa da wuri. Fahimtar ita ce kamar haka. Kusan koyaushe ana karantawa akan hanya mai mahimmanci saboda muna da umarnin jira da rubuce-rubuce ba sa kan hanya mai mahimmanci. Bugu da ƙari, sau da yawa muna karanta bayanai akan girman girman byte4 ko byte 8, yayin da toshewa shine bytes 32-128. Wannan yana nufin cewa sau da yawa muna karanta ƙaramin ɓangare na kowane toshe. Don haka ba kwa buƙatar biyan hukuncin ɗauko dukkan toshe. Yi la'akari da toshe byte 64. A yawancin hanyoyin sadarwa na kan guntu za mu iya canja wurin bytes 8 kawai a cikin zagaye ɗaya, don haka yana ɗaukar zagaye 8 don canja wurin cikakken toshe. Ana yin odar fakiti byte 8 kamar yadda adiresoshin su ke. Za mu iya canja wurin su ta wani tsari daban. Za mu iya canja wurin kalmar ƙwaƙwalwar ajiya (bytes 4 ko 8) waɗanda mai sarrafawa ko mai sarrafawa ke buƙata nan take, kuma mu canja wurin sauran kalmomin a cikin zagayowar toshewa a cikin daga baya. Wannan haɓakawa an san shi da ɗaukar kalmar mahimmanci da farko. Daga baya, mai sarrafawa zai iya sarrafa kalmar tunani, kuma ya fara aiwatar da umarnin amfani. Wannan an san shi da sake farawa tun da ba ma jiran ɗaukar sauran baitocin a cikin toshe ba. Wannan haɓakawa yana taimakawa rage hukuncin kuskure saboda muna fifita bayanan wanda ake buƙatar a aika da farko. Wannan yana da sauƙin aiwatarwa, kuma ana amfani da shi sosai. Bugu da ƙari, wannan dabarar ita ce mafi amfani lokacin da aka yi amfani da ita tsakanin cache na L1 da L2. Ba ta nuna fa'idodi masu kyau ba lokacin da hukuncin kuskure ya yi yawa. Tanadin da aka yi a cikin hukuncin kuskure ba ya shafar AMAT sosai a wannan yanayin. Na gaba, bari mu tattauna batun rubutun wanda ke rage jinkirin rubutu zuwa matakin ƙasa. Yana adana rubutu na ɗan lokaci kuma yana ba da damar shiga wasu hanyoyin shiga. Rubuta Buffer Buffer ƙaramin ma'ajiyar rubutu ne mai cikakken haɗin kai ga rubuce-rubucen da muke ƙarawa tsakanin matakai a cikin tsarin ƙwaƙwalwar ajiya, ko kuma a haɗa shi da sashin ajiya na bututun. Yawanci yana ɗauke da shigarwa 4-8 inda kowane shigarwa ke adana toshe. Fahimtar ita ce kamar haka. Saboda wurin sarari, muna yawan rubutawa zuwa kalmomi da yawa a cikin toshe ɗaya bayan ɗaya. Idan muka maimaita kuskuren kalmomi daban-daban a cikin toshe ɗaya, ba ma son aika buƙatun rubuta-rashin kuskure daban zuwa matakin ƙasa. Ya kamata mu aika saƙon rubuta-rashin kuskure guda ɗaya don toshe, kuma mu haɗa duk rubuce-rubucen. Wannan shine aikin shigarwar ma'ajiyar rubutu. Ga kowane aikin rubutu, muna ware shigarwar rubuta buffer, wanda ke ɗaukar kwararar rubuce-rubuce zuwa toshe ɗaya. Ana sarrafa shi kamar cache na yau da kullun, inda ake share tsoffin shigarwar kuma a rubuta su zuwa matakin ƙasa na tsarin ƙwaƙwalwar ajiya. Ayyukan <TECH>karanta na gaba zuwa toshe ɗaya suna samun ƙimar su daga shigarwar rubuta buffer. Sauran ayyukan karanta waɗanda ba su sami tubalan su a cikin ma'ajiyar rubutu ba za su iya ketare ma'ajiyar rubutu kuma za a iya kai tsaye zuwa tsarin jijiyoyi na ƙasa. A taƙaice, rubuta ma'ajiyar ba da damar mai sarrafawa ko motsawa gaba da sauran buƙatun ƙwaƙwalwa, rage matsin lamba akan tsarin ƙwaƙwalwa ta hanyar haɗa ayyukan rubutu zuwa toshe ɗaya, kuma za su iya yin hidimar buƙatun karanta cikin sauri idan an sami bayanan su a cikin ma'ajiyar rubutu. Yanzu da muka sami kyakkyawar fahimtar ma'ajiyar bayanai a cikin masu sarrafawa na zamani, bari mu ci gaba da fahimtar ma'ajiyar bayanai ta ciki a Sashe na 7.3. Kafin wannan ya kamata mu fahimci manufar ƙwaƙwalwar ajiya ta kama-da-wane.
